WEBVTT

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:51.120
Most people consider life a battle, but it is not a battle, it is a game. It is a game, however, which cannot be played successfully without the knowledge of spiritual law. And the Old and the New Testaments give the rules of the game with wonderful clearness. Jesus Christ taught that it was a great game of giving and receiving.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:01:19.060
Whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap. This means that whatever man sends out in word or deed will return to him. What he gives he will receive. If he gives hate he will receive hate. If he gives love he will receive love. If he gives criticism he will receive criticism. If he lies he will be lied to.

00:01:19.060 --> 00:01:29.520
If he cheats he will be cheated. We are taught also that the imaging faculty plays a leading part in the game of life.

00:01:30.820 --> 00:01:47.700
Keep thy heart, or imagination, with all diligence, for out of it are the issues of life. Proverbs 423. This means that what man images, sooner or later, externalizes in his affairs.

00:01:47.700 --> 00:02:04.340
I know of a man who feared a certain disease. It was a very rare disease, and difficult to get, but he pictured it continually and read about it until it manifested in his body and he died, the victim of distorted imagination.

00:02:04.340 --> 00:02:28.620
So we see, to play successfully the game of life, we must train the imaging faculty. A person with an imaging faculty trained to image only good brings into his life every righteous desire of his heart. Health, wealth, love, friends, perfect self-expression, his highest ideals.

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:55.100
The imagination has been called the scissors of the mind, and it is ever cutting, cutting, day by day, the pictures man sees there, and sooner or later he meets his own creations in his outer world. To train the imagination successfully, man must understand the workings of his mind. The Greeks said, know thyself.

00:02:55.940 --> 00:03:14.340
There are three departments of the mind, the subconscious, conscious, and superconscious. The subconscious is simply power without direction. It is like steam or electricity, and it does what it is directed to. It has no power of induction.

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:43.520
Whatever man feels deeply or images clearly is impressed upon the subconscious mind and carried out in minutest detail. For example, a woman I know, when a child, always made believe she was a widow. She dressed up in black clothes and wore a long black veil, and people thought she was very clever and amusing. She grew up and married a man with whom she was deeply in love.

00:03:43.520 --> 00:04:01.320
In a short time he died, and she wore black, and a sweeping veil, for many years. The picture of herself as a widow was so impressed upon the subconscious mind and in due time worked itself out, regardless of the havoc created.

00:04:01.320 --> 00:04:21.080
The conscious mind has been called mortal or carnal mind. It is the human mind and sees life as it appears to be. It sees death, disaster, sickness, poverty, and the limitation of every kind, and it impresses the subconscious.

00:04:21.080 --> 00:04:40.220
The superconscious mind is the God mind within each man and is the realm of perfect ideas. In it is the perfect pattern spoken of by Plato, the divine design, for there is a divine design for each person.

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:50.480
There is a place that you are to fill, and no one else can fill, something you are to do, which no one else can do.

00:04:51.720 --> 00:05:15.360
There is a perfect picture of this in the superconscious mind. It usually flashes across the conscious as an unattainable ideal, something too good to be true. In reality, it is man's true destiny, or destination, flashed to him from the infinite intelligence which is within himself.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:29.260
Many people, however, are in ignorance of their true destinies and are striving for things and situations which do not belong to them and would only bring failure and dissatisfaction if attained.

00:05:32.620 --> 00:05:43.800
For example, a woman came to me and asked me to speak the word that she would marry a certain man with whom she was very much in love. She called him A.B.

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:57.020
I replied that this would be a violation of spiritual law, but that I would speak the word for the right man, the divine selection, the man who belonged to her by divine right.

00:05:57.020 --> 00:06:06.780
I added, If A.B. is the right man, you can't lose him, and if he isn't, you will receive his equivalent.

00:06:07.940 --> 00:06:19.200
She saw A.B. frequently, but no headway was made in their friendship. One evening she called and said, Do you know, for the last week A.B. hasn't seemed so wonderful to me?

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:25.700
I replied, Maybe he is not the divine selection. Another man may be the right one.

00:06:26.900 --> 00:06:42.020
Soon after that she met another man, who fell in love with her at once, and who said she was his ideal. In fact, he said all the things that she had always wished A.B. would say to her. She remarked, It was quite uncanny.

00:06:42.020 --> 00:06:57.040
She soon returned to his love and lost all interest in A.B. This shows the law of substitution. A right idea was substituted for a wrong one. Therefore, there was no loss or sacrifice involved.

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:07.440
Jesus Christ said, Seek ye first the kingdom of God and his righteousness, and all these things shall be added unto you.

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:27.820
And he said, The kingdom was within man. The kingdom is the realm of right ideas, or the divine pattern. Jesus Christ taught that man's words played a leading part in the game of life. By your words ye are justified, and by your words ye are condemned.

00:07:30.540 --> 00:07:41.120
Many people have brought disaster into their lives through idle words. For example, a woman once asked me why her life was now one of poverty, of limitation.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:56.940
Formerly she had a home, was surrounded by beautiful things, and had plenty of money. We found she had often tired of the management of her home, and had said repeatedly, I am sick and tired of things. I wish I lived in a trunk.

00:07:56.940 --> 00:08:11.460
And she added, Today I am living in that trunk. She had spoken herself into a trunk. The subconscious mind has no sense of humor, and people often joke themselves into unhappy experiences.

00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:27.120
For example, a woman who had a great deal of money joked continually about getting ready for the poorhouse. In a few years she was almost destitute, having impressed the subconscious mind with a picture of lack and limitation.

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:34.940
Fortunately the law works both ways, and a situation of lack may be changed to one of plenty.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:49.520
For example, a woman came to me one hot summer's day for a treatment for prosperity. She was worn out, dejected, and discouraged. She said she possessed just eight dollars in the world.

00:08:49.520 --> 00:09:03.080
I said, Good, we'll bless the eight dollars and multiply them as Jesus Christ multiplied the loaves and the fishes. For he taught that every man had the power to bless and to multiply, to heal and to prosper.

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:25.520
She said, What shall I do next? I replied, Follow intuition. Have you a hunch to do anything or to go anywhere? Intuition means in-tuition, or to be taught from within. It is man's unerring guide, and I will deal more fully with its laws in a following chapter.

00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:46.420
The woman replied, I don't know. I seem to have a hunch to go home. I've just enough money for car fare. Her home was in a distant city, and was one of lack and limitation, and the reasoning mind, or intellect, would have said stay in New York and get work and make some money.

00:09:46.420 --> 00:10:06.180
I replied, Then go home. Never violate a hunch. I spoke the following words for her. Infinite Spirit, open the way for great abundance for, hmm, she is an irresistible magnet for all that belongs to her by divine right.

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:29.560
I told her to repeat it continually also. She left for home immediately. In calling on a woman one day, she linked up with an old friend of her family. Through this friend she received thousands of dollars in a most miraculous way. She has said to me often, Tell people about the woman who came to you with eight dollars and a hunch.

00:10:29.560 --> 00:10:46.620
There is always plenty on man's pathway, but it can only be brought into manifestation through desire, faith, or the spoken word. Jesus Christ brought out clearly that man must make the first move.

00:10:47.780 --> 00:11:07.120
Ask, and it shall be given to you. Seek, and ye shall find. Knock, and it shall be opened unto you. Matthew 7.7. In the scriptures we read, Concerning the works of my hands, command ye me.

00:11:08.420 --> 00:11:25.400
Infinite intelligence, God, is ever ready to carry out man's smallest or greatest demands. Every desire, uttered or unexpressed, is a demand. We are often startled by having a wish suddenly fulfilled.

00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:38.960
For example, one Easter, having seen many beautiful rose trees in the florist's windows, I wished I would receive one, and for an instant saw it mentally being carried in the door.

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:53.260
Easter came, and with it a beautiful rose tree. I thanked my friend the following day and told her it was just what I had wanted. She replied, I didn't send you a rose tree, I sent you lilies.

00:11:53.260 --> 00:12:12.020
The man had mixed the order, and sent me a rose tree simply because I had started the law in action, and I had to have a rose tree. Nothing stands between man and his highest ideals, and every desire of his heart, but doubt and fear.

00:12:12.020 --> 00:12:40.240
When man can wish without worrying, every desire will be instantly fulfilled. I will explain more fully in a following chapter the scientific reason for this, and how fear must be erased from the consciousness. It is man's only enemy. Fear of lack, fear of failure, fear of sickness, fear of loss, and a feeling of insecurity on some plane.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:13:01.240
Jesus Christ said, Why are ye fearful, O ye of little faith? Matthew 8.26. So we can see we must substitute faith for fear, for fear is only inverted faith. It is faith in evil instead of good.

00:13:02.300 --> 00:13:17.220
The object of the game of life is to see clearly one's good and to obliterate all mental pictures of evil. This must be done by impressing the subconscious mind with a realization of good.

00:13:17.220 --> 00:13:37.480
A very brilliant man who has attained great success told me he had suddenly erased all fear from his consciousness by reading a sign which hung in a room. He saw printed in large letters this statement, Why worry, it will probably never happen.

00:13:37.480 --> 00:13:52.560
These words were stamped indelibly upon his subconscious mind, and he now has a firm conviction that only good can come into his life, and therefore only good can manifest.

00:13:53.300 --> 00:14:10.860
In the following chapter I will deal with the different methods of impressing the subconscious mind. It is man's faithful servant, but one must be careful to give it the right orders. Man has ever a silent listener at his side, his subconscious mind.

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:33.140
Every thought, every word is impressed upon it and carried out in amazing detail. It is like a singer making a record on the sensitive disc of the phonographic plate. Every note and tone of the singer's voice is registered. If he coughs or hesitates, it is registered also.

00:14:33.140 --> 00:14:51.180
So let us break all the old bad records in the subconscious mind, the records of our lives which we do not wish to keep, and make new and beautiful ones. Speak these words aloud with power and conviction.

00:14:52.980 --> 00:15:11.340
I now smash and demolish, by my spoken word, every untrue record in my subconscious mind. They shall return to the dust heap of their native nothingness, for they came from my own vain imaginings.

00:15:11.340 --> 00:15:27.000
I now make my perfect records through the Christ within, the records of health, wealth, love, and perfect self-expression. This is the square of life, the game completed.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:50.640
In the following chapters, I will show how man can change his conditions by changing his words. Any man who does not know the power of the word is behind the times. Death and life are in the power of the tongue. Proverbs 18-21.

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:57.860
Amy Conger.

00:16:24.444 --> 00:16:26.704
THE LAW OF PROSPERITY.

00:16:33.304 --> 00:16:39.424
One of the greatest messages given to the race through the scriptures is that God is

00:16:39.424 --> 00:16:46.264
man's supply and that man can release, through his spoken word, all that belongs to him by

00:16:46.264 --> 00:16:47.064
divine right.

00:16:47.604 --> 00:16:51.504
He must, however, have perfect faith in his spoken word.

00:16:52.424 --> 00:16:59.844
Isaiah said, My word shall not return unto me void, but shall accomplish that whereunto

00:16:59.844 --> 00:17:00.644
it is sent.

00:17:01.404 --> 00:17:08.284
We know now that words and thoughts are a tremendous vibratory force, ever moulding

00:17:08.284 --> 00:17:10.184
man's body and affairs.

00:17:11.184 --> 00:17:16.204
A woman came to me in great distress and said she was to be sued on the fifteenth of the

00:17:16.204 --> 00:17:17.804
month for three thousand dollars.

00:17:18.384 --> 00:17:22.044
She knew no way of getting the money and was in despair.

00:17:22.944 --> 00:17:29.064
I told her that God was her supply and that there is a supply for every demand.

00:17:29.624 --> 00:17:31.344
So I spoke the word.

00:17:32.024 --> 00:17:36.804
I gave thanks that the woman would receive three thousand dollars at the right time

00:17:36.804 --> 00:17:37.984
in the right way.

00:17:38.544 --> 00:17:43.284
I told her she must have perfect faith and act her perfect faith.

00:17:43.824 --> 00:17:47.364
The fifteenth came, but no money had materialized.

00:17:48.084 --> 00:17:51.764
She called me on the phone and asked what she was to do.

00:17:52.304 --> 00:17:56.444
I replied, It is Saturday, so they won't sue you today.

00:17:57.064 --> 00:18:02.864
Your part is to act rich, thereby showing perfect faith that you will receive it by

00:18:02.864 --> 00:18:03.184
Monday.

00:18:04.064 --> 00:18:07.624
She asked me to lunch with her to keep her courage.

00:18:08.224 --> 00:18:13.544
When I joined her at a restaurant, I said, This is no time to economize.

00:18:13.824 --> 00:18:19.124
Order an expensive luncheon and act as if you have already received the three thousand

00:18:19.124 --> 00:18:19.784
dollars.

00:18:20.904 --> 00:18:25.424
All things whatsoever, ye ask in prayer, believing ye shall receive.

00:18:26.504 --> 00:18:30.544
You must act as if you had already received.

00:18:31.604 --> 00:18:35.844
The next morning she called me on the phone and asked me to stay with her during the day.

00:18:35.844 --> 00:18:40.964
I said, No, you are divinely protected and God is never too late.

00:18:42.204 --> 00:18:48.184
In the evening she phoned again, greatly excited, and said, My dear, a miracle has

00:18:48.184 --> 00:18:48.704
happened.

00:18:48.904 --> 00:18:52.604
I was sitting in my room this morning when the doorbell rang.

00:18:53.504 --> 00:18:56.304
I said to the maid, Don't let anyone in.

00:18:56.704 --> 00:19:00.984
The maid, however, looked out the window and said, It's your cousin with the long white

00:19:00.984 --> 00:19:01.404
beard.

00:19:02.164 --> 00:19:05.264
So I said, Call him back, I would like to see him.

00:19:05.264 --> 00:19:10.564
And he was just turning the corner when he heard the maid's voice and he came back.

00:19:11.684 --> 00:19:16.964
He talked for about an hour and just as he was leaving he said, Oh, by the way, how are

00:19:16.964 --> 00:19:17.664
finances?

00:19:18.504 --> 00:19:23.864
I told him I needed the money and he said, My dear, I will give you three thousand dollars

00:19:23.864 --> 00:19:25.064
the first of the month.

00:19:25.864 --> 00:19:28.964
I didn't like to tell him that I was going to be sued.

00:19:29.464 --> 00:19:30.624
What shall I do?

00:19:31.004 --> 00:19:35.244
I won't receive it till the first of the month and I must have it tomorrow.

00:19:35.904 --> 00:19:38.604
I said, I'll keep on treating.

00:19:40.184 --> 00:19:43.024
I said, Spirit is never too late.

00:19:43.604 --> 00:19:50.224
I give thanks that she has received the money on the invisible plane and that it manifests

00:19:50.224 --> 00:19:51.424
on time.

00:19:52.844 --> 00:19:57.664
The next morning her cousin called her up and said, Come to my office this morning and

00:19:57.664 --> 00:19:59.044
I will give you the money.

00:19:59.644 --> 00:20:04.884
That afternoon she had three thousand dollars to her credit in the bank and wrote checks

00:20:04.884 --> 00:20:07.404
as rapidly as her excitement would permit.

00:20:08.504 --> 00:20:14.464
If one asks for success and prepares for failure, he will get the situation he has prepared

00:20:14.464 --> 00:20:14.924
for.

00:20:15.484 --> 00:20:20.944
For example, a man came to me asking me to speak the word that a certain debt would be

00:20:20.944 --> 00:20:21.604
wiped out.

00:20:21.924 --> 00:20:26.764
I found he spent his time planning what he would say to the man when he did not pay his

00:20:26.764 --> 00:20:29.284
bill, therefore neutralizing my words.

00:20:29.684 --> 00:20:32.184
He should have seen himself paying the debt.

00:20:33.624 --> 00:20:39.264
We have a wonderful illustration of this in the Bible relating to the three kings who

00:20:39.264 --> 00:20:42.744
were in the desert without water for their men and horses.

00:20:43.504 --> 00:20:48.824
They consulted the prophet Elisha who gave them this astonishing message.

00:20:49.784 --> 00:20:58.804
Thus saith the Lord, Ye shall not see wind, neither shall ye see rain, yet make this valley

00:20:58.804 --> 00:21:00.024
full of ditches.

00:21:01.944 --> 00:21:07.524
Man must prepare for the thing he has asked for when there isn't the slightest sign of

00:21:07.524 --> 00:21:08.484
it in sight.

00:21:09.384 --> 00:21:16.584
For example, a woman found it necessary to look for an apartment during the year when

00:21:16.584 --> 00:21:19.384
there was a great shortage of apartments in New York.

00:21:19.844 --> 00:21:24.984
It was considered almost an impossibility and her friends were sorry for her and said,

00:21:25.384 --> 00:21:26.724
isn't it too bad?

00:21:26.984 --> 00:21:29.764
You'll have to store your furniture and live in a hotel.

00:21:30.304 --> 00:21:33.364
She replied, you needn't feel sorry for me.

00:21:33.504 --> 00:21:36.584
I'm a superman and I'll get an apartment.

00:21:37.124 --> 00:21:42.464
She spoke the words, infinite spirit, open the way for the right apartment.

00:21:43.204 --> 00:21:49.964
She knew there was a supply for every demand and that she was unconditioned working on

00:21:49.964 --> 00:21:54.424
the spiritual plane and that one with God is a majority.

00:21:55.704 --> 00:22:03.124
She had contemplated buying new blankets when the tempter, the adverse thought or reasoning

00:22:03.124 --> 00:22:05.884
mind suggested, don't buy the blankets.

00:22:06.044 --> 00:22:10.384
Perhaps after all, you won't get an apartment and you will have no use for them.

00:22:10.944 --> 00:22:16.864
Promptly she replied to herself, I'll dig my ditches by buying the blankets.

00:22:17.584 --> 00:22:22.824
So she prepared for the apartment, acted as though she already had it.

00:22:23.804 --> 00:22:28.544
She found one in a miraculous way and it was given to her.

00:22:28.904 --> 00:22:35.444
Although there were over 200 other applicants, the blankets showed active faith.

00:22:36.404 --> 00:22:42.464
It is needless to say that the ditches dug by the three kings in the desert were filled

00:22:42.464 --> 00:22:43.524
to overflowing.

00:22:47.084 --> 00:22:53.084
Getting into the spiritual swing of things is no easy matter for the average person.

00:22:53.564 --> 00:22:57.804
The adverse thoughts of doubt and fear surge from the subconscious.

00:22:58.424 --> 00:23:03.264
They are the army of the aliens which must be put to flight.

00:23:03.724 --> 00:23:07.984
This explains why it is so often darkest before the dawn.

00:23:09.184 --> 00:23:13.684
A big demonstration is usually preceded by tormenting thoughts.

00:23:14.304 --> 00:23:20.784
Having made a statement of high spiritual truth, one challenges the old beliefs in the

00:23:20.784 --> 00:23:25.664
subconscious and error is exposed to be put out.

00:23:26.364 --> 00:23:32.964
This is the time when one must make his affirmations of truth repeatedly and rejoice and give

00:23:32.964 --> 00:23:35.164
thanks that he has already received.

00:23:36.204 --> 00:23:39.064
Before ye call, I shall answer.

00:23:40.204 --> 00:23:46.864
This means that every good and perfect gift is already man's awaiting his recognition.

00:23:47.824 --> 00:23:51.744
Man can only receive what he sees himself receiving.

00:23:53.204 --> 00:23:57.824
The children of Israel were told that they could have all the land they could see.

00:23:58.424 --> 00:24:00.524
This is true of every man.

00:24:00.524 --> 00:24:04.664
He has only the land within his own mental vision.

00:24:05.824 --> 00:24:11.784
Every great work, every big accomplishment has been brought into manifestation through

00:24:11.784 --> 00:24:18.244
holding to the vision, and often, just before the big achievement, comes apparent failure

00:24:18.244 --> 00:24:19.404
and discouragement.

00:24:20.524 --> 00:24:26.184
The children of Israel, when they reached the promised land, were afraid to go in, for

00:24:26.184 --> 00:24:30.044
they said it was filled with giants who made them feel like grasshoppers.

00:24:30.524 --> 00:24:37.204
And there we saw the giants, and we were in our own sight as grasshoppers.

00:24:38.124 --> 00:24:40.884
This is almost every man's experience.

00:24:41.304 --> 00:24:48.584
However, the one who knows spiritual law is undisturbed by appearance and rejoices

00:24:48.584 --> 00:24:51.144
while he is yet in captivity.

00:24:51.784 --> 00:24:57.604
That is, he holds to his vision and gives thanks that the end is accomplished.

00:24:57.924 --> 00:24:59.304
He has received.

00:25:00.604 --> 00:25:04.104
Jesus Christ gave a wonderful example of this.

00:25:04.584 --> 00:25:06.024
He said to his disciples,

00:25:06.744 --> 00:25:12.364
Say not ye, there are yet four months, and then cometh the harvest.

00:25:13.244 --> 00:25:19.984
Behold, I say unto you, lift up your eyes and look on the fields, for they are ripe

00:25:19.984 --> 00:25:21.464
already to harvest.

00:25:23.884 --> 00:25:29.644
His clear vision pierced the world of matter, and he saw clearly the fourth

00:25:29.644 --> 00:25:36.204
dimensional world, things as they really are, perfect and complete in divine mind.

00:25:37.004 --> 00:25:43.284
So man must ever hold the vision of his journey's end and demand the manifestation

00:25:43.284 --> 00:25:45.924
of that which he has already received.

00:25:46.684 --> 00:25:54.484
It may be his perfect health, love, supply, self-expression, home, or friends.

00:25:56.504 --> 00:26:04.064
They are all finished and perfect ideas, registered in divine mind, man's own

00:26:04.064 --> 00:26:09.144
super-conscious mind, and must come through him, not to him.

00:26:09.784 --> 00:26:14.044
For example, a man came to me asking for treatments for success.

00:26:14.504 --> 00:26:20.224
It was his imperative that he raise within a certain time $50,000 for his business.

00:26:20.224 --> 00:26:24.944
The time limit was almost up when he came to see me in despair.

00:26:25.824 --> 00:26:31.624
No one wanted to invest in his enterprise, and the bank had flatly refused a loan.

00:26:32.384 --> 00:26:37.504
I replied, I suppose you lost your temper while at the bank, therefore your power.

00:26:38.004 --> 00:26:41.844
You can control any situation if you first control yourself.

00:26:43.224 --> 00:26:46.564
Go back to the bank, I added, and I will treat.

00:26:47.444 --> 00:26:55.224
My treatment was, you are identified in love with the spirit of everyone connected with the bank.

00:26:55.884 --> 00:27:00.344
Let the divine idea come out of this situation.

00:27:01.664 --> 00:27:05.684
He replied, woman, you are talking about an impossibility.

00:27:06.124 --> 00:27:13.124
Tomorrow is Saturday, the bank closes at 12, and my train won't get me there until 10,

00:27:13.124 --> 00:27:18.264
and the time limit is up tomorrow, and anyway they won't do it, it's too late.

00:27:18.944 --> 00:27:24.824
I replied, God doesn't need any time and is never too late.

00:27:25.344 --> 00:27:27.284
With him, all things are possible.

00:27:29.524 --> 00:27:34.604
I added, I don't know anything about business, but I know all about God.

00:27:35.164 --> 00:27:39.504
He replied, it all sounds fine when I sit here listening to you,

00:27:39.504 --> 00:27:41.884
but when I go out, it's terrible.

00:27:42.604 --> 00:27:46.284
He lived in a distant city, and I did not hear from him for a week.

00:27:46.504 --> 00:27:47.524
Then came a letter.

00:27:48.484 --> 00:27:51.364
It read, you were right, I raised the money,

00:27:51.544 --> 00:27:55.484
and I will never again doubt the truth of all that you have told me.

00:27:56.264 --> 00:27:59.084
I saw him a few weeks later, and I said, what happened?

00:27:59.364 --> 00:28:02.044
You evidently had plenty of time after all.

00:28:02.304 --> 00:28:07.704
He replied, my train was late, and I got there just 15 minutes to 12.

00:28:08.484 --> 00:28:13.104
I walked into the bank quietly, and I said, I have come for the loan,

00:28:13.684 --> 00:28:16.184
and they gave it to me without a question.

00:28:17.744 --> 00:28:21.184
It was the last 15 minutes of the time allotted to him,

00:28:21.644 --> 00:28:24.024
and infinite spirit was not too late.

00:28:24.584 --> 00:28:28.184
In this instance, the man could never have demonstrated alone.

00:28:28.464 --> 00:28:31.044
He needed someone to help him hold the vision.

00:28:31.564 --> 00:28:33.784
This is what one man can do for another.

00:28:35.084 --> 00:28:38.044
Jesus Christ knew the truth of this when he said,

00:28:38.664 --> 00:28:43.204
if two of you shall agree on earth as touching anything that they shall ask,

00:28:43.324 --> 00:28:46.844
it shall be done for them of my Father which is in heaven.

00:28:48.544 --> 00:28:52.924
One gets too close to his own affairs and becomes doubtful and fearful.

00:28:53.584 --> 00:28:59.084
The friend or healer sees clearly the success, health, or prosperity,

00:28:59.324 --> 00:29:03.764
and never wavers because he is not close to the situation.

00:29:04.544 --> 00:29:09.364
It is much easier to demonstrate for someone else than for oneself,

00:29:10.064 --> 00:29:15.104
so a person should not hesitate to ask for help if he feels himself wavering.

00:29:15.964 --> 00:29:18.324
A keen observer of life once said,

00:29:18.904 --> 00:29:23.764
no man can fail if some one person sees him successful.

00:29:24.984 --> 00:29:29.924
Such is the power of the vision, and many a great man has owed his success

00:29:29.924 --> 00:29:34.584
to a wife or a sister or a friend who believed in him

00:29:34.584 --> 00:29:38.584
and held without wavering to the perfect pattern.

00:30:16.781 --> 00:30:23.841
By thy words thou shalt be justified, and by thy words thou shalt be condemned.

00:30:25.101 --> 00:30:31.261
A person knowing the power of the word becomes very careful of his conversation. He has only

00:30:31.261 --> 00:30:38.261
to watch the reaction of his words to know that they do not return void. Through his spoken word,

00:30:38.261 --> 00:30:43.121
man is continually making laws for himself. I knew a man who said,

00:30:43.641 --> 00:30:50.121
I always miss a car. It invariably pulls out just as I arrive. His daughter said,

00:30:50.361 --> 00:30:57.141
I always catch a car. It's sure to come just as I get there. This occurred for years. Each had

00:30:57.141 --> 00:31:03.501
made a separate law for himself, one of failure, one of success. This is the psychology of

00:31:03.501 --> 00:31:11.441
superstitions. The horseshoe or rabbit's foot contains no power, but man's spoken word and

00:31:11.441 --> 00:31:17.961
belief that it will bring him good luck creates expectancy in the subconscious mind and attracts

00:31:17.961 --> 00:31:26.221
a lucky situation. I find, however, this will not work when a man has advanced spiritually and knows

00:31:26.941 --> 00:31:36.921
One cannot turn back, and one must put away graven images. For example, two men in my class

00:31:36.921 --> 00:31:43.741
had had great success in business for several months, when suddenly everything went to smash.

00:31:44.341 --> 00:31:50.581
We tried to analyze the situation and I found, instead of making their affirmations and looking

00:31:50.581 --> 00:31:57.981
to God for success and prosperity, they had each bought a lucky monkey. And I said,

00:31:58.041 --> 00:32:05.841
oh, I see, you have been trusting in the lucky monkeys instead of God. Put away the lucky monkeys

00:32:05.841 --> 00:32:12.961
and call on the law of forgiveness, for man has power to forgive or neutralize his mistakes.

00:32:13.941 --> 00:32:20.401
They decided to throw the lucky monkeys down a coal hole, and all went well again. This

00:32:20.401 --> 00:32:26.421
does not mean, however, that one should throw away every lucky ornament or horseshoe about

00:32:26.421 --> 00:32:32.621
the house, but he must recognize that the power back of it is the one and only power, God,

00:32:33.001 --> 00:32:40.541
and that the object simply gives him a feeling of expectancy. I was with a friend one day who was

00:32:40.541 --> 00:32:46.841
in deep despair. In crossing the street, she picked up a horseshoe. Immediately she was filled

00:32:46.841 --> 00:32:52.901
with joy and hope. She said God had sent her the horseshoe in order to keep up her courage.

00:32:53.741 --> 00:32:59.061
It was indeed at that moment about the only thing that could have registered in her consciousness.

00:32:59.961 --> 00:33:06.501
Her hope became faith, and she ultimately made a wonderful demonstration. I wish to make the point

00:33:06.501 --> 00:33:13.901
clear that the men previously mentioned they were depending on the monkeys alone, while this woman

00:33:13.901 --> 00:33:21.801
recognized the power back of the horseshoe. I know, in my own case, it took a long while to

00:33:21.801 --> 00:33:28.041
get out of a belief that a certain thing brought disappointment. If the thing happened, disappointment

00:33:28.041 --> 00:33:34.421
invariably followed. I found the only way I could make a change in the subconscious was by asserting,

00:33:35.001 --> 00:33:41.741
there are not two powers, there is only one power, God. Therefore, there are no disappointments,

00:33:41.741 --> 00:33:49.621
and this means a happy surprise. I noticed a change at once, and happy surprises commenced

00:33:49.621 --> 00:33:56.521
coming my way. I have a friend who said nothing could induce her to walk under a ladder. I said,

00:33:56.881 --> 00:34:05.801
if you are afraid, you are giving into a belief in two powers, good and evil, instead of one. As God

00:34:05.801 --> 00:34:14.721
is absolute, there can be no opposing power unless man makes the false of evil for himself. To show

00:34:14.721 --> 00:34:21.421
you believe in only one power, God, and that there is no power or reality in evil, walk under the

00:34:21.421 --> 00:34:28.521
next ladder you see. Soon after, she went to her bank. She wished to open her box in the safety

00:34:28.521 --> 00:34:36.541
deposit vault, and there stood a ladder on her pathway. It was impossible to reach the box without

00:34:36.541 --> 00:34:43.681
passing under the ladder. She quailed with fear and turned back. She could not face the lion on

00:34:43.681 --> 00:34:51.441
her pathway. However, when she reached the street, my words rang in her ears, and she decided to turn

00:34:51.441 --> 00:34:58.101
and walk under it. It was a big moment in her life, for ladders had held her in bondage for

00:34:58.101 --> 00:35:05.341
years. She retraced her steps to the vault, and the ladder was no longer there. This so often

00:35:05.341 --> 00:35:12.401
happens. If one is willing to do a thing that he is afraid to do, he does not have to. It is the law

00:35:12.401 --> 00:35:20.401
of non-resistance, which is so little understood. Someone has said that courage contains genius and

00:35:20.401 --> 00:35:28.081
magic. Face a situation fearlessly, and there is no situation to face. It falls away of its own

00:35:28.081 --> 00:35:35.561
weight. The explanation is that fear attracted the ladder on the woman's pathway, and fearlessness

00:35:35.561 --> 00:35:42.201
removed it. Thus, the invisible forces are ever working for the man who is always pulling the

00:35:42.201 --> 00:35:49.441
strings himself, though he does not know it. Owing to the vibratory power of words, whatever man

00:35:49.441 --> 00:35:57.801
voices, he begins to attract. People who continually speak of disease invariably attract it. After

00:35:57.801 --> 00:36:06.661
man knows the truth, he cannot be too careful of his words. For example, I have a friend who often

00:36:06.661 --> 00:36:14.601
says on the phone, do come to see me and have a fine old-fashioned chat. This old-fashioned chat

00:36:14.601 --> 00:36:24.181
means an hour of about 500 to 1,000 destructive words, the principal topics being loss, lack,

00:36:24.181 --> 00:36:31.861
failure, and sickness. I reply, no, thank you. I've had enough old-fashioned chats in my life. They

00:36:31.861 --> 00:36:39.501
are too expensive, but I will be glad to have a new-fashioned chat and talk about what we want,

00:36:39.921 --> 00:36:46.781
not what we don't want. There is an old saying that man only dares to use his words for three

00:36:46.781 --> 00:36:55.181
purposes, to heal, bless, or prosper. What man says of others will be said of him, and what he

00:36:55.181 --> 00:37:01.241
wishes for another he is wishing for himself. Curses like chickens come home to roost.

00:37:03.621 --> 00:37:10.441
If a man wishes someone bad luck, he is sure to attract bad luck himself. If he wishes to

00:37:10.441 --> 00:37:18.921
aid someone to success, he is wishing and aiding himself to success. The body may be renewed and

00:37:18.921 --> 00:37:25.781
transformed through the spoken word and clear vision, and disease be completely wiped out of

00:37:25.781 --> 00:37:32.581
the consciousness. The metaphysician knows that all disease has a mental correspondence, and in

00:37:32.581 --> 00:37:39.441
order to heal the body, one must first heal the soul. The soul is the subconscious mind,

00:37:39.441 --> 00:37:45.401
and it must be saved from wrong thinking. In the 23rd Psalm we read,

00:37:45.721 --> 00:37:52.441
He restoreth my soul. This means that the subconscious mind or soul must be restored

00:37:52.441 --> 00:37:59.041
with the right ideas, and the mystical marriage is the marriage of the soul and the spirit,

00:37:59.401 --> 00:38:06.881
or the subconscious and super-conscious mind. They must be one. When the subconscious is flooded

00:38:06.881 --> 00:38:15.581
with the perfect ideas of the super-conscious, God and man are one. I and the Father are one.

00:38:16.201 --> 00:38:23.541
That is, he is one with the realm of perfect ideas. He is the man made in God's likeness and image,

00:38:23.641 --> 00:38:30.621
imagination, and is given power and dominion over all created things, his mind, body, and affairs.

00:38:31.421 --> 00:38:38.841
It is safe to say that all sickness and unhappiness come from the violation of the law of love. A new

00:38:38.841 --> 00:38:45.881
commandment I give unto you, love one another. And in the game of life, love or goodwill takes

00:38:45.881 --> 00:38:54.521
every trick. For example, a woman I know had, for years, an appearance of a terrible skin disease.

00:38:54.521 --> 00:39:01.501
The doctors told her it was incurable, and she was in despair. She was on the stage,

00:39:01.621 --> 00:39:07.001
and she feared she would soon have to give up her profession, and she had no other means of

00:39:07.001 --> 00:39:15.801
support. She, however, procured a good engagement, and on the opening night made a great hit. She

00:39:15.801 --> 00:39:22.821
received flattering notices from the critics, and was joyful and elated. The next day she received

00:39:22.821 --> 00:39:30.321
a notice of dismissal. A man in the cast had been jealous of her success and had caused her to be

00:39:30.321 --> 00:39:38.121
sent away. She felt hatred and resentment taking complete possession of her, and she cried out,

00:39:38.401 --> 00:39:47.421
Oh God, don't let me hate that man. That night she worked for hours in the silence. She said,

00:39:47.801 --> 00:39:55.101
I soon came into a very deep silence. I seemed to be at peace with myself, with the man,

00:39:55.381 --> 00:40:01.461
and with the whole world. I continued this for two following nights, and on the third day,

00:40:02.121 --> 00:40:09.461
I found I was healed completely of the skin disease. In asking for love or goodwill,

00:40:09.561 --> 00:40:16.001
she had fulfilled the law. For love is the fulfilling of the law, and the disease which

00:40:16.001 --> 00:40:24.581
came from the subconscious resentment was wiped out. Continual criticism produces rheumatism,

00:40:25.021 --> 00:40:31.561
as critical, inharmonious thoughts cause unnatural deposits in the blood which settle in the joints.

00:40:32.881 --> 00:40:40.821
False growths are caused by jealousy, hatred, unforgiveness, fear, etc. Every disease is caused

00:40:40.821 --> 00:40:47.561
by a mind not at ease. I said once in my class, there is no use asking anyone,

00:40:48.121 --> 00:40:53.661
what's the matter with you? We might as well just say, who's the matter with you?

00:40:54.941 --> 00:41:00.181
Unforgiveness is the most prolific cause of disease. It will harden arteries or

00:41:00.181 --> 00:41:05.041
liver and affect the eyesight. In its train are endless ills.

00:41:07.461 --> 00:41:13.521
I called on a woman one day, who said she was ill from having eaten a poisoned oyster. I

00:41:13.521 --> 00:41:20.421
replied, oh no, the oyster was harmless. You poisoned the oyster. What's the matter with you?

00:41:21.081 --> 00:41:28.441
She answered, oh, about nineteen people. She had quarreled with nineteen people,

00:41:28.441 --> 00:41:36.961
and had become so inharmonious that she attracted the wrong oyster. Any inharmonie on the external

00:41:36.961 --> 00:41:45.921
indicates there is mental inharmonie. As the within, so the without. Man's only enemies are

00:41:45.921 --> 00:41:55.181
within himself, and a man's foes shall be they of his own household. Personality is one of the

00:41:55.181 --> 00:42:03.161
enemies to be overcome, as this planet is taking its initiation in love. It was Christ's message,

00:42:03.561 --> 00:42:09.901
peace on earth, goodwill toward man. The enlightened man, therefore, endeavors to

00:42:09.901 --> 00:42:15.981
perfect himself upon his neighbor. His work is within himself to send out goodwill and

00:42:15.981 --> 00:42:23.121
blessings to every man, and the marvelous thing is that if one blesses a man, he has no power

00:42:23.121 --> 00:42:30.561
to harm him. For example, a man came to me asking him to treat for success in business. He was

00:42:30.561 --> 00:42:36.241
selling machinery, and a rival appeared on the scene with what he proclaimed was a better machine,

00:42:36.761 --> 00:42:44.281
and my friend feared defeat. I said, first of all, we must wipe out all fear, and know that

00:42:44.281 --> 00:42:51.861
God protects your interests, and that the divine idea must come out of the situation. That is,

00:42:51.861 --> 00:43:00.061
the right machine will be sold by the right man to the right man. And I added, don't hold one

00:43:00.061 --> 00:43:05.901
critical thought toward that man. Bless him all day, and be willing not to sell your machine if

00:43:05.901 --> 00:43:13.461
it isn't the divine idea. So he went to the meeting, fearless and non-resistant, and blessing

00:43:13.461 --> 00:43:20.061
the other man. He said the outcome was very remarkable. The other man's machine refused to

00:43:20.061 --> 00:43:27.621
work, and he sold his without the slightest difficulty. But I say unto you, love your enemies,

00:43:28.141 --> 00:43:35.921
bless them that curse you, do good to them that hate you, and pray for them which spitefully use

00:43:35.921 --> 00:43:45.001
you and persecute you. Goodwill produces a great aura of protection about the one who sends it,

00:43:45.001 --> 00:43:53.221
and no weapon that is formed against him shall prosper. In other words, love and goodwill destroy

00:43:53.221 --> 00:44:01.581
the enemies within oneself, therefore one has no enemies on the external. There is peace on earth

00:44:01.581 --> 00:44:10.361
for him who sends goodwill to man.

00:44:36.747 --> 00:44:40.807
THE LAW OF NON RESISTANCE.

00:44:40.807 --> 00:44:47.447
RESIST NOT EVIL. BE NOT OVERCOME OF EVIL, BUT OVERCOME EVIL WITH GOOD.

00:44:48.847 --> 00:44:52.447
Nothing on earth can resist an absolutely non-resistant person.

00:44:53.107 --> 00:44:58.787
The Chinese say that water is the most powerful element because it is perfectly non-resistant.

00:44:59.467 --> 00:45:03.367
It can wear away a rock and sleep away all before it.

00:45:04.267 --> 00:45:12.787
Jesus Christ said, resist not evil, for he knew in reality there is no evil, therefore nothing to resist.

00:45:13.587 --> 00:45:19.967
Evil has come of man's vain imagination or a belief in two powers, good and evil.

00:45:20.887 --> 00:45:30.507
There is an old legend that Adam and Eve ate of Maya, the tree of illusion, and saw two powers instead of one power, God.

00:45:30.507 --> 00:45:39.007
Therefore, evil is a false law man has made for himself through psychoma or soul-sleep.

00:45:39.647 --> 00:45:54.787
Soul-sleep means that man's soul has been hypnotized by the race-belief of sin, sickness and death, etc., which is carnal or mortal thought, and his affairs have out-pictured his illusions.

00:45:58.627 --> 00:46:10.827
We have read in a preceding chapter that man's soul is his subconscious mind, and whatever he feels deeply, good or bad, is out-pictured by that faithful servant.

00:46:11.647 --> 00:46:15.647
His body and affairs show forth what he has been picturing.

00:46:16.227 --> 00:46:22.707
The sick man has pictured sickness, the poor man poverty, the rich man wealth.

00:46:23.527 --> 00:46:31.407
Young people often say, why does a little child attract illness when it is too young to even know what it means?

00:46:32.587 --> 00:46:41.247
I answer that children are sensitive and receptive to the thoughts of others about them, and often out-picture the fears of their parents.

00:46:42.207 --> 00:46:49.907
I heard a metaphysician once say, if you do not run your subconscious mind yourself, someone else will run it for you.

00:46:50.587 --> 00:47:01.507
Mothers often, unconsciously, attract illness and disaster to their children by continually holding them in thoughts of fear and watching for symptoms.

00:47:02.347 --> 00:47:09.647
For example, a friend asked a woman if her little girl had had the measles. She replied promptly, not yet.

00:47:10.327 --> 00:47:17.987
This implied that she was expecting the illness and therefore preparing the way for what she did not want for herself and child.

00:47:17.987 --> 00:47:26.507
However, the man who is centered and established in his right thinking, the man who sends out only goodwill to his fellow man,

00:47:26.627 --> 00:47:32.667
and who is without fear, cannot be touched or influenced by the negative thoughts of others.

00:47:33.267 --> 00:47:39.567
In fact, he could then receive only good thoughts, as he himself sends forth only good thoughts.

00:47:40.467 --> 00:47:45.327
Resistance is hell, for it places man in a state of torment.

00:47:45.327 --> 00:47:52.647
A metaphysician once gave me a wonderful recipe for taking every trick in the game of life.

00:47:53.167 --> 00:47:57.887
It is the acme of non-resistance. He gave it in this way.

00:47:58.707 --> 00:48:04.307
At one time in my life, I baptized children, and of course they had many names.

00:48:04.927 --> 00:48:13.507
Now I no longer baptize children, but I baptize events. But I give every event the same name.

00:48:13.507 --> 00:48:22.887
If I have a failure, I baptize it success, in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost.

00:48:24.007 --> 00:48:29.767
In this we see the great law of transmutation, founded on non-resistance.

00:48:30.427 --> 00:48:35.327
Through his spoken word, every failure was transmuted into success.

00:48:35.327 --> 00:48:42.707
For example, a woman who required money, who knew the spiritual law of opulence,

00:48:43.147 --> 00:48:48.627
was thrown continually in a business way with a man who made her feel very poor.

00:48:49.127 --> 00:48:54.067
He talked lack and limitation, and she commenced to catch his poverty thoughts.

00:48:54.347 --> 00:48:58.307
So she disliked him, and blamed him for her failure.

00:48:58.307 --> 00:49:04.167
She knew in order to demonstrate her supply, she must first feel that she had received.

00:49:04.647 --> 00:49:08.347
A feeling of opulence must precede its manifestation.

00:49:09.487 --> 00:49:16.187
It dawned upon her one day that she was resisting the situation, and seeing two powers instead of one.

00:49:16.607 --> 00:49:22.647
So she blessed the man and baptized the situation. Success, she affirmed.

00:49:22.647 --> 00:49:30.527
As there is only one power, God, this man is here for my good, and my prosperity.

00:49:31.267 --> 00:49:34.027
Just what he did not seem to be there for.

00:49:34.747 --> 00:49:42.347
Soon after that, she met, through this man, a woman who gave her, for a service rendered, several thousand dollars,

00:49:42.627 --> 00:49:47.827
and the man moved to a distant city, and faded harmoniously from her life.

00:49:47.827 --> 00:49:53.227
Make the statement, every man is a golden link in the chain of my good,

00:49:53.747 --> 00:50:03.547
for all men are God in manifestation, awaiting the opportunity given by man himself to serve the divine plan of his life.

00:50:04.667 --> 00:50:07.727
Bless your enemy, and you rob him of his ammunition.

00:50:08.867 --> 00:50:11.547
His arrows will be transmuted into blessings.

00:50:11.547 --> 00:50:15.707
This law is true of nations as well as individuals.

00:50:16.567 --> 00:50:23.087
Bless a nation, send love and goodwill to every inhabitant, and it is robbed of its power to harm.

00:50:23.987 --> 00:50:28.947
Man can only get the right idea of non-resistance through spiritual understanding.

00:50:29.727 --> 00:50:33.447
My students have often said, I don't want to be a doormat.

00:50:33.887 --> 00:50:40.727
I reply, when you use non-resistance with wisdom, no one will ever be able to walk over you.

00:50:40.727 --> 00:50:47.507
Another example, one day I was impatiently awaiting an important telephone call.

00:50:48.027 --> 00:50:52.827
I resisted every call that came in and made no outgoing calls myself,

00:50:53.247 --> 00:50:56.127
reasoning that it might interfere with the one I was awaiting.

00:50:57.187 --> 00:51:03.647
Instead of saying, divine ideas never conflict, the call will come at the right time,

00:51:04.127 --> 00:51:10.147
leaving it to infinite intelligence to arrange, I commenced to manage things myself.

00:51:10.147 --> 00:51:15.367
I made the battle mine, not God's, and remained tense and anxious.

00:51:16.047 --> 00:51:20.127
The bell did not ring for about an hour, and I glanced at the phone

00:51:20.127 --> 00:51:25.607
and found the receiver had been off that length of time, and the phone was disconnected.

00:51:26.827 --> 00:51:33.167
My anxiety, fear, and belief in interference had brought on a total eclipse of the telephone.

00:51:33.807 --> 00:51:38.487
Realizing what I had done, I commenced blessing the situation at once.

00:51:38.487 --> 00:51:45.887
I baptized it success, and affirmed, I cannot lose any call that belongs to me by divine right.

00:51:46.307 --> 00:51:49.087
I am under grace, and not under law.

00:51:50.347 --> 00:51:55.087
A friend rushed out to the nearest telephone to notify the company to reconnect.

00:51:55.867 --> 00:52:02.187
She entered a crowded grocery, but the proprietor left his customers and attended to the call himself.

00:52:02.867 --> 00:52:08.227
My phone was connected at once, and two minutes later I received a very important call,

00:52:08.227 --> 00:52:12.247
and about an hour afterward, the one I had been awaiting.

00:52:13.487 --> 00:52:16.647
One's ships come in over a calm sea.

00:52:17.627 --> 00:52:21.847
So long as man resists a situation, he will have it with him.

00:52:22.367 --> 00:52:26.027
If he runs away from it, it will run after him.

00:52:26.667 --> 00:52:31.147
For example, I repeated this to a woman one day, and she replied,

00:52:31.147 --> 00:52:34.627
How true that is! I was unhappy at home.

00:52:34.907 --> 00:52:38.287
I disliked my mother, who was critical and domineering.

00:52:38.507 --> 00:52:40.447
So I ran away and was married.

00:52:40.767 --> 00:52:44.667
But I married my mother, for my husband was exactly like my mother,

00:52:44.967 --> 00:52:48.067
and I had the same situation to face again.

00:52:49.107 --> 00:52:51.767
Agree with thine adversary quickly.

00:52:53.047 --> 00:52:56.787
That means, agree that the adverse situation is good.

00:52:56.787 --> 00:53:00.947
Be undisturbed by it, and it falls away of its own weight.

00:53:01.667 --> 00:53:05.607
None of these things move me, is a wonderful affirmation.

00:53:06.907 --> 00:53:12.247
The inharmonious situation comes from some inharmony within man himself.

00:53:12.947 --> 00:53:18.207
When there is in him no emotional response to an inharmonious situation,

00:53:18.507 --> 00:53:21.207
it fades away forever from his pathway.

00:53:22.027 --> 00:53:24.767
So we see man's work is ever with himself.

00:53:25.427 --> 00:53:30.247
People have said to me, Give treatments to change my husband or my brother.

00:53:30.867 --> 00:53:34.907
I reply, No, I will give treatments to change you.

00:53:35.427 --> 00:53:39.307
When you change, your husband and your brother will change.

00:53:40.227 --> 00:53:42.547
One of my students was in the habit of lying.

00:53:43.227 --> 00:53:47.687
I told her it was a failure method, and if she lied, she would be lied to.

00:53:47.967 --> 00:53:52.587
She replied, I don't care. I can't possibly get along without lying.

00:53:53.487 --> 00:53:58.207
One day she was speaking on the phone to a man with whom she was very much in love.

00:53:58.627 --> 00:54:01.767
She turned to me and said, I don't trust him.

00:54:01.927 --> 00:54:03.887
I know he's lying to me.

00:54:04.207 --> 00:54:08.967
I replied, Well, you lie yourself, so someone has to lie to you,

00:54:09.527 --> 00:54:14.007
and you will be sure it will be just the person you want the truth of.

00:54:15.127 --> 00:54:19.107
Sometime after that I saw her and she said, I'm cured of lying.

00:54:19.107 --> 00:54:22.307
I questioned, What cured you?

00:54:22.827 --> 00:54:26.987
She replied, I've been living with a woman who lied worse than I did.

00:54:27.947 --> 00:54:31.107
One is often cured of his faults by seeing them in others.

00:54:31.887 --> 00:54:36.447
Life is a mirror, and we find only ourselves reflected in our associates.

00:54:37.327 --> 00:54:41.987
Living in the past is a failure method and a violation of spiritual law.

00:54:42.907 --> 00:54:46.967
Jesus Christ said, Behold, now is the accepted time.

00:54:46.967 --> 00:54:49.407
Now is the day of salvation.

00:54:50.647 --> 00:54:54.307
Lot's wife looked back and was turned into a pillar of salt.

00:54:55.367 --> 00:54:58.427
The robbers of time are the past and the future.

00:54:59.047 --> 00:55:03.507
Man should bless the past and forget it, if it keeps him in bondage,

00:55:03.787 --> 00:55:08.727
and bless the future, knowing it has in store for him endless joys.

00:55:08.927 --> 00:55:11.627
But live fully in the now.

00:55:12.507 --> 00:55:17.067
For example, a woman came to me complaining that she had no money

00:55:17.067 --> 00:55:19.107
with which to buy Christmas gifts.

00:55:19.507 --> 00:55:22.007
She said, Last year was so different.

00:55:22.247 --> 00:55:25.367
I had plenty of money and gave lovely presents,

00:55:25.707 --> 00:55:28.147
and this year I scarcely have a cent.

00:55:28.767 --> 00:55:31.947
I replied, You will never demonstrate money

00:55:31.947 --> 00:55:34.447
while you are pathetic and live in the past.

00:55:35.147 --> 00:55:39.707
Live fully in the now and get ready to give Christmas presents.

00:55:39.707 --> 00:55:42.587
Dig your ditches and the money will come.

00:55:43.387 --> 00:55:45.687
She exclaimed, I know what to do.

00:55:45.967 --> 00:55:50.407
I'll buy some tinsel, twine, Christmas seals, and wrapping paper.

00:55:51.027 --> 00:55:54.807
I replied, Do that and the presents will come

00:55:54.807 --> 00:55:57.507
and stick themselves to the Christmas seals.

00:55:58.587 --> 00:56:02.447
This too was showing financial fearlessness and faith in God,

00:56:02.847 --> 00:56:06.147
as the reasoning mind said, Keep every cent you have

00:56:06.147 --> 00:56:08.447
as you are not sure you will get any more.

00:56:08.447 --> 00:56:12.027
She bought her seals, paper, and twine,

00:56:12.347 --> 00:56:16.427
and a few days before Christmas received a gift of several hundred dollars.

00:56:17.167 --> 00:56:21.647
Buying the seals and twine had impressed the subconscious with expectancy

00:56:21.647 --> 00:56:25.267
and opened the way for the manifestation of the money.

00:56:25.887 --> 00:56:29.167
She purchased all the presents in plenty of time.

00:56:30.947 --> 00:56:33.607
Man must live suspended in the moment.

00:56:33.607 --> 00:56:36.987
Look well, therefore, to this day.

00:56:37.207 --> 00:56:39.387
Such is the salutation of the dawn.

00:56:40.607 --> 00:56:44.447
He must be spiritually alert, ever waiting his leads,

00:56:44.947 --> 00:56:46.807
taking advantage of every opportunity.

00:56:48.027 --> 00:56:51.207
One day I said continually, silently,

00:56:52.007 --> 00:56:54.927
Infinite Spirit, don't let me miss a trick.

00:56:55.527 --> 00:56:58.707
And something very important was told to me that evening.

00:56:59.087 --> 00:57:03.067
It is most necessary to begin the day with the right words.

00:57:03.067 --> 00:57:07.067
Make an affirmation immediately upon waking.

00:57:07.627 --> 00:57:08.667
For example,

00:57:09.267 --> 00:57:11.107
Thy will be done this day.

00:57:11.487 --> 00:57:13.427
Today is a day of completion.

00:57:14.107 --> 00:57:16.607
I give thanks for this perfect day.

00:57:17.207 --> 00:57:21.367
Miracles shall follow miracles, and wonders shall never cease.

00:57:22.767 --> 00:57:27.607
Make this a habit, and one will see wonders and miracles come into his life.

00:57:28.427 --> 00:57:30.727
One morning I picked up a book and read,

00:57:30.727 --> 00:57:34.267
Look with wonder at that which is before you.

00:57:34.947 --> 00:57:39.407
It seemed to be my message for the day, so I repeated it again and again.

00:57:40.127 --> 00:57:43.207
Look with wonder at that which is before you.

00:57:43.867 --> 00:57:47.587
At about noon a large sum of money was given to me,

00:57:47.627 --> 00:57:50.327
which I had been desiring for a certain purpose.

00:57:51.607 --> 00:57:56.467
In the following chapter I will give affirmations that I have found most effective.

00:57:56.467 --> 00:58:01.667
However, one should never use an affirmation unless it is absolutely satisfying

00:58:01.667 --> 00:58:04.447
and convincing to his own consciousness,

00:58:04.867 --> 00:58:08.267
and often an affirmative is changed to suit different people.

00:58:08.387 --> 00:58:11.967
For example, the following has brought success to many.

00:58:12.727 --> 00:58:15.987
I have a wonderful work, in a wonderful way.

00:58:16.467 --> 00:58:19.407
I give wonderful service for wonderful pay.

00:58:20.307 --> 00:58:24.727
I gave the first two lines to one of my students, and she added the last two.

00:58:24.727 --> 00:58:27.867
It made a most powerful statement,

00:58:28.267 --> 00:58:31.607
as there should always be perfect payment for perfect service,

00:58:31.867 --> 00:58:34.987
and a rhyme sinks easily into the subconscious.

00:58:35.687 --> 00:58:41.067
She went about singing it aloud, and soon did receive wonderful work in a wonderful way

00:58:41.067 --> 00:58:43.627
and gave wonderful service for wonderful pay.

00:58:44.647 --> 00:58:48.427
Another student, a businessman, took it and changed the word to business.

00:58:48.827 --> 00:58:49.647
He repeated,

00:58:49.647 --> 00:58:53.067
I have a wonderful business, in a wonderful way,

00:58:53.267 --> 00:58:56.287
and I give wonderful service for wonderful pay.

00:58:56.947 --> 00:59:00.407
That afternoon he made a $41,000 deal,

00:59:00.787 --> 00:59:04.067
though there had been no activity in his affairs for months.

00:59:05.027 --> 00:59:10.107
Every affirmation must be carefully worded and completely cover the ground.

00:59:10.667 --> 00:59:15.787
For example, I knew a woman who was in great need and made a demand for work.

00:59:15.787 --> 00:59:19.767
She received a great deal of work, but was never paid anything.

00:59:20.287 --> 00:59:23.827
She now knows to add wonderful service for wonderful pay.

00:59:24.687 --> 00:59:29.027
It is man's divine right to have plenty, more than enough.

00:59:29.947 --> 00:59:34.127
His barns should be full, and his cup should flow over.

00:59:34.867 --> 00:59:36.747
This is God's idea for man,

00:59:36.927 --> 00:59:41.347
and when man breaks down the barriers of lack in his own consciousness,

00:59:41.347 --> 00:59:47.507
the Golden Age will be his, and every righteous desire of his heart fulfilled.

00:59:57.558 --> 01:00:21.598
5. The Law of Karma and the Law of Forgiveness

01:00:24.298 --> 01:00:31.758
Man receives only that which he gives. The game of life is a game of boomerangs. Man's thoughts,

01:00:31.918 --> 01:00:38.818
deeds, and words return to him sooner or later, with astounding accuracy. This is the law of

01:00:38.818 --> 01:00:48.878
karma, which is Sanskrit for comeback. Whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap. For example,

01:00:48.878 --> 01:00:53.878
a friend told me this story of herself illustrating the law. She said,

01:00:54.598 --> 01:01:01.518
I make all my karma on my aunt. Whatever I say to her, someone says to me. I am often

01:01:01.518 --> 01:01:07.958
irritable at home when one day said to my aunt who was talking to me during dinner,

01:01:08.878 --> 01:01:14.578
no more talk, I wish to eat in peace. The following day I was lunching with a woman

01:01:14.578 --> 01:01:19.458
with whom I wished to make a great impression. I was talking animatedly when she said,

01:01:19.698 --> 01:01:25.158
no more talk, I wish to eat in peace. My friend is high in consciousness,

01:01:25.258 --> 01:01:32.758
so her karma returns much more quickly than to one on the mental plane. The more man knows,

01:01:32.918 --> 01:01:38.138
the more he is responsible for, and a person with a knowledge of spiritual law,

01:01:38.138 --> 01:01:42.418
which he does not practice, suffers greatly in consequence.

01:01:43.558 --> 01:01:51.358
The fear of the Lord, law, is the beginning of wisdom. If we read the word Lord, law,

01:01:51.898 --> 01:01:54.758
it will make many passages in the Bible much clearer.

01:01:56.058 --> 01:02:04.618
Vengeance is mine, I will repay, saith the Lord, law. It is the law which takes vengeance, not God.

01:02:04.618 --> 01:02:12.758
God sees man perfect, created in his own image, imagination, and given power and dominion.

01:02:13.798 --> 01:02:20.478
This is the perfect idea of man, registered in divine mind, awaiting man's recognition,

01:02:20.958 --> 01:02:27.538
for man can only be what he sees himself to be, and only attain what he sees himself attaining.

01:02:28.258 --> 01:02:32.378
Nothing ever happens without an onlooker, is an ancient saying.

01:02:33.298 --> 01:02:40.338
Man first sees his failure or success, his joy or sorrow, before it swings into visibility,

01:02:40.618 --> 01:02:46.798
from the scenes set in his own imagination. We have observed this in the mother picturing

01:02:46.798 --> 01:02:53.238
disease for her child, or a woman seeing success for her husband. Jesus Christ said,

01:02:53.238 --> 01:02:59.518
Ye shall know the truth, and the truth shall make you free. So we see freedom,

01:02:59.718 --> 01:03:05.318
from all unhappy conditions, comes through knowledge, a knowledge of spiritual law.

01:03:06.378 --> 01:03:12.778
Obedience precedes authority, and the law obeys man when he obeys the law.

01:03:13.358 --> 01:03:20.578
The law of electricity must be obeyed before it becomes man's servant. When handled ignorantly,

01:03:20.578 --> 01:03:28.938
it becomes man's deadly foe, so with the laws of mind. For example, a woman with a strong personal

01:03:28.938 --> 01:03:34.838
will, wished she owned a house which belonged to an acquaintance, and she often made mental

01:03:34.838 --> 01:03:41.258
pictures of herself living in the house. In the course of time, the man died, and she moved into

01:03:41.258 --> 01:03:47.058
the house. Several years afterwards, coming into the knowledge of spiritual law, she said to me,

01:03:47.058 --> 01:03:54.838
Do you think I had anything to do with that man's death? I replied, Yes, your desire was so strong,

01:03:55.098 --> 01:04:01.178
everything made way for it. But you paid your karmic debt, your husband, whom you loved

01:04:01.178 --> 01:04:07.978
devotedly, died soon after, and the house was a white elephant on your hands for many years.

01:04:09.178 --> 01:04:13.318
The original owner, however, could not have been affected by her thoughts,

01:04:13.318 --> 01:04:19.698
had he been positive in the truth, nor her husband, but they were both under karmic law.

01:04:20.478 --> 01:04:24.458
The woman should have said, feeling the great desire for the house,

01:04:25.438 --> 01:04:30.318
Infinite intelligence, give me the right house, equally as charming as this,

01:04:30.758 --> 01:04:36.718
the house which is mine by divine right. The divine selection would have given perfect

01:04:36.718 --> 01:04:42.858
satisfaction, and brought good to all. The divine pattern is the only safe pattern to work by.

01:04:43.318 --> 01:04:50.618
Desire is a tremendous force, and must be directed in the right channels, or chaos ensues.

01:04:51.718 --> 01:04:59.158
In demonstrating, the most important step is the first step, to ask a right. Man should always

01:04:59.158 --> 01:05:06.138
demand only that which is his by divine right. To go back to the illustration, had the woman

01:05:06.138 --> 01:05:15.058
taken this attitude. If this house, I desire, is mine, I cannot lose it. If it is not, give me

01:05:15.058 --> 01:05:21.358
its equivalent. The man might have decided to move out harmoniously, had it been the divine

01:05:21.358 --> 01:05:27.598
selection for her, or another house would have been substituted. Anything forced into manifestation

01:05:27.598 --> 01:05:33.698
through personal will is always ill-got, and has ever-bad success.

01:05:35.298 --> 01:05:43.218
Man is admonished, my will be done, not thine. And the curious thing is, man always gets just

01:05:43.218 --> 01:05:49.638
what he desires, when he does relinquish all personal will, thereby enabling infinite

01:05:49.638 --> 01:05:55.898
intelligence to work through him. Stand ye still, and see the salvation of the Lord,

01:05:55.898 --> 01:06:03.238
law. For example, a woman came to me in great distress. Her daughter had determined to take

01:06:03.238 --> 01:06:09.858
a very hazardous trip, and the mother was filled with fear. She said she had used every argument,

01:06:10.338 --> 01:06:16.238
had pointed out the dangers to be encountered, had forbidden her to go, but the daughter became

01:06:16.238 --> 01:06:22.678
more and more rebellious and determined. I said to the mother, you are forcing your personal will

01:06:22.678 --> 01:06:29.078
upon your daughter, which you have no right to do, and your fear of the trip is only attracting

01:06:29.078 --> 01:06:37.478
it, for man attracts what he fears. I added, let go and take your mental hands off,

01:06:37.918 --> 01:06:46.458
put it in God's hands, and use this statement. I put this situation in the hands of infinite

01:06:46.458 --> 01:06:53.638
love and wisdom. If this trip is the divine plan, I bless it and no longer resist,

01:06:54.118 --> 01:07:00.478
but if it is not divinely planned, I give thanks that it is now dissolved and dissipated.

01:07:01.898 --> 01:07:07.078
A day or two after that, her daughter said to her, mother, I have given up the trip.

01:07:07.738 --> 01:07:14.778
And the situation returned to its native nothingness. It is learning to stand still,

01:07:14.778 --> 01:07:21.338
which seems so difficult for man. I will deal more fully with this law in the chapter on

01:07:21.338 --> 01:07:27.918
non-resistance. I will give another example of sowing and reaping which came in the most

01:07:27.918 --> 01:07:34.338
curious way. A woman came to me saying she had received a counterfeit twenty dollar bill

01:07:34.338 --> 01:07:41.598
given to her at the bank. She was much disturbed for, she said, the people at the bank will never

01:07:41.598 --> 01:07:49.198
acknowledge their mistake. I replied, let us analyze the situation and find out why you

01:07:49.198 --> 01:07:56.438
attracted it. She thought a few moments and exclaimed, I know it. I sent a friend a lot of

01:07:56.438 --> 01:08:03.678
stage money just for a joke. So the law had sent her some stage money, for it doesn't know anything

01:08:03.678 --> 01:08:12.058
about jokes. I said, now we will call on the law of forgiveness and neutralize the situation.

01:08:13.498 --> 01:08:18.198
Christianity is founded upon the law of forgiveness. Christ has redeemed us from

01:08:18.198 --> 01:08:23.978
the curse of the karmic law, and the Christ within each man is his redeemer and salvation

01:08:23.978 --> 01:08:31.878
from all inharmonious conditions. So I said, infinite spirit, we call on the law of forgiveness

01:08:31.878 --> 01:08:38.898
and give thanks that she is under grace and not under law and cannot lose this twenty dollars

01:08:38.898 --> 01:08:46.738
which is hers by divine right. Now I said, go back to the bank and tell them fearlessly

01:08:46.738 --> 01:08:54.498
that it was given you there by mistake. She obeyed and, to her surprise, they apologized

01:08:54.498 --> 01:09:00.978
and gave her another bill treating her most courteously. So knowledge of the law gives man

01:09:00.978 --> 01:09:07.538
power to rub out his mistakes. Man cannot force the external to be what he is not.

01:09:08.078 --> 01:09:12.098
If he desires riches, he must be rich first in consciousness.

01:09:13.958 --> 01:09:20.538
For example, a woman came to me asking treatment for prosperity. She did not take much interest

01:09:20.538 --> 01:09:27.458
in her household affairs and her home was in great disorder. I said to her, if you wish to be rich,

01:09:27.458 --> 01:09:34.058
you must be orderly. All men with great wealth are orderly, and order is heaven's first law.

01:09:34.538 --> 01:09:39.838
I added, you will never become rich with a burnt match in the pincushion.

01:09:41.098 --> 01:09:45.478
She had a good sense of humor and commenced immediately putting her house in order.

01:09:45.998 --> 01:09:52.218
She rearranged furniture, straightened out her bureau drawers, cleaned rugs, and soon made a big

01:09:52.218 --> 01:10:00.018
financial demonstration, a gift from a relative. The woman herself became made over and keeps

01:10:00.018 --> 01:10:07.778
herself keyed up financially by being ever watchful of the external and expecting prosperity knowing

01:10:07.778 --> 01:10:15.398
God is her supply. Many people are in ignorance of the fact that gifts and things are investments

01:10:15.398 --> 01:10:20.638
and that hoarding and saving invariably lead to loss.

01:10:21.718 --> 01:10:29.338
There is that scattereth and yet increaseth. There is that withholdeth more than is meat,

01:10:29.818 --> 01:10:37.878
but it tendeth to poverty. For example, I knew a man who wanted to buy a fur-lined overcoat.

01:10:38.218 --> 01:10:44.658
He and his wife went to various shops, but there was none he wanted. He said they were all too

01:10:44.658 --> 01:10:53.178
cheap looking. At last he was shown one the salesman said was valued at $1,000, but which the manager

01:10:53.178 --> 01:11:00.678
would sell him for $500 as it was late in the season. His financial possessions amounted to

01:11:00.678 --> 01:11:07.918
about $700. The reasoning mind would have said, you can't afford to spend nearly all you have on a

01:11:07.918 --> 01:11:14.518
coat. But he was very intuitive and never reasoned. He turned to his wife and said,

01:11:15.118 --> 01:11:21.358
if I get this coat, I'll make a ton of money. So his wife consented weekly.

01:11:22.918 --> 01:11:28.658
About a month later, he received a $10,000 commission. The coat made him feel so rich

01:11:28.658 --> 01:11:34.278
it linked him with success and prosperity. Without the coat, he would not have received

01:11:34.278 --> 01:11:41.638
the commission. It was an investment paying large dividends. If man ignores these leadings

01:11:41.638 --> 01:11:48.178
to spend or to give, the same amount of money will go in an uninteresting or unhappy way.

01:11:48.518 --> 01:11:55.298
For example, a woman told me on Thanksgiving Day she informed her family that they could not afford

01:11:55.298 --> 01:12:02.438
a Thanksgiving dinner. She had the money, but decided to save it. A few days later, someone

01:12:02.438 --> 01:12:07.618
entered her room and took from the bureau drawer the exact amount the dinner would have cost.

01:12:08.478 --> 01:12:15.498
The law always stands back of the man who spends fearlessly with wisdom. For example,

01:12:15.858 --> 01:12:21.678
one of my students was shopping with her little nephew. The child clamored for a toy which she

01:12:21.678 --> 01:12:28.238
told him she could not afford to buy. She realized suddenly that she was seeking lack and not

01:12:28.238 --> 01:12:35.578
recognizing God as her supply. So she bought the toy and on her way home, picked up in the street

01:12:35.578 --> 01:12:42.838
the exact amount of money she had paid for it. Man's supply is inexhaustible and unfailing when

01:12:42.838 --> 01:12:49.858
fully trusted, but faith or trust must precede the demonstration. According to your faith,

01:12:50.258 --> 01:12:58.218
be it unto you. Faith is the substance of things hoped for and the evidence of things not seen.

01:12:58.898 --> 01:13:06.158
For faith holds the vision steady and the adverse pictures are dissolved and dissipated and

01:13:06.158 --> 01:13:14.758
in due season we shall reap if we faint not. Jesus Christ brought the good news, the gospel,

01:13:15.178 --> 01:13:21.418
that there was a higher law than the law of karma and that that law transcends the law of karma.

01:13:21.418 --> 01:13:29.538
It is the law of grace or forgiveness. It is the law which frees man from the law of cause and

01:13:29.538 --> 01:13:40.138
effect, the law of consequence. Under grace, not under law. We are told that on this plain,

01:13:40.758 --> 01:13:47.398
man reaps where he has not sown. The gifts of God are simply poured out upon him.

01:13:48.278 --> 01:13:54.538
All that the kingdom affords is his. This continued state of bliss

01:13:54.538 --> 01:14:03.058
awaits the man who has overcome the race or world thought. In the world thought there is tribulation

01:14:03.058 --> 01:14:12.018
but as Jesus Christ said, be of good cheer. I have overcome the world. The world thought is

01:14:12.018 --> 01:14:19.618
of sin, sickness and death. He saw their absolute unreality and said sickness and sorrow shall pass

01:14:19.618 --> 01:14:28.498
away and death itself, the last enemy, be overcome. We now know from a scientific standpoint that death

01:14:28.498 --> 01:14:34.818
could be overcome by stamping the subconscious mind with the conviction of eternal youth and

01:14:34.818 --> 01:14:44.098
life. The subconscious, being simply power without direction, carries out orders without questioning.

01:14:45.358 --> 01:14:49.918
Working under the direction of the super-conscious, the Christ or God within man,

01:14:50.498 --> 01:14:58.098
the resurrection of the body would be accomplished. Man would no longer throw off his body in death.

01:14:58.098 --> 01:15:02.258
It would be transformed into the body electric,

01:15:02.578 --> 01:15:11.258
sung by Walt Whitman, for Christianity is founded upon the forgiveness of sins and an empty tomb.

01:15:45.550 --> 01:15:49.030
Casting the Burden. Impressing the Subconscious.

01:15:50.330 --> 01:15:56.570
When man knows his own powers and the workings of his mind, his great desire is to find an easy

01:15:56.570 --> 01:16:03.030
and quick way to impress the subconscious with good, for simply an intellectual knowledge of

01:16:03.030 --> 01:16:10.250
the truth will not bring results. In my own case, I found the easiest way is in casting the burden.

01:16:11.050 --> 01:16:15.030
A metaphysician once explained it in this manner. He said,

01:16:15.510 --> 01:16:22.250
The only thing which gives anything weight in nature is the law of gravitation. And if a boulder

01:16:22.250 --> 01:16:28.390
could be taken high above the planet, there would be no weight in that boulder. And that is what

01:16:28.390 --> 01:16:36.670
Jesus Christ meant when he said, My yoke is easy and my burden is light. He had overcome the world

01:16:37.410 --> 01:16:43.550
and functioned in the fourth dimensional realm, where there is only perfection, completion, life

01:16:43.550 --> 01:16:53.250
and joy. He said, Come to me, all ye that labor and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest.

01:16:54.290 --> 01:17:03.170
Take my yoke upon you, for my yoke is easy and my burden is light. We are also told in the 55th

01:17:03.170 --> 01:17:10.490
Psalm to cast thy burden upon the Lord. Many passages in the Bible state that the battle

01:17:10.490 --> 01:17:19.450
is God's, not man's, and that man is always to stand still and see the salvation of the Lord.

01:17:20.290 --> 01:17:26.470
This indicates that the super-conscious mind, or Christ within, is the department which fights

01:17:26.470 --> 01:17:34.230
man's battle and relieves him of his burdens. We see, therefore, that man violates law if he

01:17:34.230 --> 01:17:41.210
carries a burden, and a burden is an adverse thought or condition, and this thought or condition

01:17:41.210 --> 01:17:48.050
has its root in the subconscious. It seems almost impossible to make any headway directing the

01:17:48.050 --> 01:17:53.570
subconscious from the conscious or reasoning mind, as the reasoning mind, the intellect,

01:17:53.570 --> 01:18:00.070
is limited in its conceptions and filled with doubts and fears. How scientific is it, then,

01:18:00.070 --> 01:18:07.270
to cast the burden upon the super-conscious mind, or Christ within, where it is made light or

01:18:07.270 --> 01:18:13.190
dissolved into its native nothingness? For example, a woman in urgent need of money

01:18:13.190 --> 01:18:18.250
may light upon the Christ within, the super-conscious with the statement,

01:18:18.250 --> 01:18:25.310
I cast this burden of lack on the Christ within, and I go free to have plenty.

01:18:26.810 --> 01:18:33.670
The belief in lack was her burden, and as she cast it upon the super-conscious with its belief

01:18:33.670 --> 01:18:42.570
of plenty, an avalanche of supply was the result. We read, the Christ in you, the hope of glory.

01:18:44.050 --> 01:18:50.530
Another example. One of my students had been given a new piano, and there was no room in her

01:18:50.530 --> 01:18:56.390
studio for it until she had moved out the old one. She was in a state of perplexity.

01:18:56.690 --> 01:19:03.230
She wanted to keep the old piano, but knew of no place to send it. She became desperate,

01:19:03.590 --> 01:19:10.770
as the new piano was to be sent immediately, in fact, was on its way, with no place to put it.

01:19:10.770 --> 01:19:17.750
She said it came to her to repeat, I cast this burden on the Christ within, and I go free.

01:19:18.910 --> 01:19:24.830
A few minutes later, her phone rang, and a woman friend asked if she might rent her old piano,

01:19:25.230 --> 01:19:33.050
and it was moved out, a few minutes before the new one arrived. I knew a woman whose burden was

01:19:33.050 --> 01:19:39.930
resentment. She said, I cast this burden of resentment on the Christ within, and I go free

01:19:39.930 --> 01:19:48.190
to be loving, harmonious, and happy. The Almighty Superconscious flooded the subconscious with love,

01:19:48.970 --> 01:19:53.910
and her whole life was changed. For years, resentment had held her in a state of torment

01:19:53.910 --> 01:20:00.550
and imprisoned her soul, the subconscious mind. The statement should be made over and over and

01:20:00.550 --> 01:20:07.550
over, sometimes for hours at a time, silently or audibly, with quietness, but determination.

01:20:08.510 --> 01:20:16.110
I have often compared it to winding up a Victrola. We must wind ourselves up with spoken words.

01:20:17.070 --> 01:20:22.730
I have noticed in casting the burden, after a little while, one seems to see clearly.

01:20:23.490 --> 01:20:31.110
It is impossible to have clear vision while in the throes of carnal mind. Doubts and fear poison

01:20:31.110 --> 01:20:36.830
the mind and body, and imagination runs riot, attracting disaster and disease.

01:20:37.650 --> 01:20:44.230
In steadily repeating the affirmation, I cast this burden on the Christ within, and go free.

01:20:44.890 --> 01:20:51.430
The vision clears, and with it a feeling of relief, and sooner or later comes the manifestation of

01:20:51.430 --> 01:20:58.550
good, be it health, happiness, or supply. One of my students once asked me to explain the

01:20:58.550 --> 01:21:04.490
darkness before the dawn. I referred in a preceding chapter to the fact that often,

01:21:04.850 --> 01:21:11.270
before the big demonstration, everything seems to go wrong, and deep depression clouds the

01:21:11.270 --> 01:21:17.850
consciousness. It means that out of the subconscious are rising the doubts and fears of the ages.

01:21:18.490 --> 01:21:25.930
These old derelicts of the subconscious rise to the surface, to be put out. It is then that man

01:21:25.930 --> 01:21:33.230
should clap his cymbals, like Jehoshaphat, and give thanks that he is saved, even though he seems

01:21:33.230 --> 01:21:39.230
surrounded by the enemy, the situation of lack or disease. The student continued,

01:21:39.710 --> 01:21:47.110
How long must one remain in the dark? And I replied, Until one can see in the dark.

01:21:47.830 --> 01:21:52.050
And casting the burden enables one to see in the dark.

01:21:52.910 --> 01:22:01.350
In order to impress the subconscious, active faith is always essential. Faith without works is dead.

01:22:02.010 --> 01:22:05.850
In these chapters, I have endeavored to bring out this point.

01:22:07.970 --> 01:22:14.670
Jesus Christ showed active faith when he commanded the multitude to sit down on the ground

01:22:14.670 --> 01:22:21.530
before he gave thanks for the loaves and the fishes. I will give another example showing

01:22:21.530 --> 01:22:29.750
how necessary this step is. In fact, active faith is the bridge over which man passes to his

01:22:29.750 --> 01:22:37.290
promised land. Through misunderstanding, a woman had been separated from her husband, whom she loved

01:22:37.290 --> 01:22:44.070
deeply. He refused all offers of reconciliation and would not communicate with her in any way.

01:22:44.930 --> 01:22:49.550
Coming into the knowledge of spiritual law, she denied the appearance of separation.

01:22:49.550 --> 01:22:56.050
She made this statement, There is no separation in divine mind. Therefore,

01:22:56.630 --> 01:23:02.310
I cannot be separated from the love and companionship which are mine by divine right.

01:23:03.410 --> 01:23:10.750
She showed active faith by arranging a place for him at the table every day, thereby impressing

01:23:10.750 --> 01:23:17.970
the subconscious with a picture of his return. Over a year passed, but she never wavered,

01:23:17.970 --> 01:23:20.610
and one day he walked in.

01:23:22.470 --> 01:23:28.990
The subconscious is often impressed through music. Music has a fourth-dimensional quality

01:23:28.990 --> 01:23:34.910
and releases the soul from imprisonment. It makes wonderful things seem possible,

01:23:35.310 --> 01:23:41.990
and easy of accomplishment. I have a friend who uses her Victrola daily for this purpose.

01:23:41.990 --> 01:23:49.850
It puts her in perfect harmony and releases the imagination. Another woman often dances while

01:23:49.850 --> 01:23:56.610
making her affirmations. The rhythm and harmony of music and motion carry her words forth with

01:23:56.610 --> 01:24:04.310
tremendous power. The student must remember also not to despise the day of small things.

01:24:05.150 --> 01:24:12.410
Invariably, before a demonstration come signs of land. Before Columbus reached America,

01:24:12.630 --> 01:24:20.330
he saw birds and twigs which showed him land was near. So it is with a demonstration, but often the

01:24:20.330 --> 01:24:27.050
student mistakes it for the demonstration itself and is disappointed. For example, a woman had

01:24:27.050 --> 01:24:33.610
spoken the word for a set of dishes. Not long afterwards, a friend gave her a dish which was

01:24:33.610 --> 01:24:40.770
cracked. She came to me and said, well, I asked for a set of dishes and all I got was a cracked

01:24:40.770 --> 01:24:48.130
plate. I replied, the plate was only signs of land. It shows your dishes are coming.

01:24:48.590 --> 01:24:53.790
Look upon it as birds and seaweed. And not long afterwards, the dishes came.

01:24:55.110 --> 01:25:00.770
Continually making believe impresses the subconscious. If one makes believe he is

01:25:01.390 --> 01:25:09.250
and makes believe he is successful, in due time he will reap. Children are always making believe

01:25:09.250 --> 01:25:17.010
and except ye be converted and become as little children, you shall not enter the kingdom of

01:25:17.010 --> 01:25:24.290
heaven. For example, I know of a woman who was very poor, but no one could make her feel poor.

01:25:24.290 --> 01:25:30.670
She earned a small amount of money from rich friends who constantly reminded her of her poverty

01:25:30.670 --> 01:25:37.470
and to be careful and saving. Regardless of their admonitions, she would spend all her earnings on a

01:25:37.470 --> 01:25:44.490
hat or make someone a gift and be in a rapturous state of mind. Her thoughts were always centered

01:25:44.490 --> 01:25:52.290
on beautiful clothes and rings and things, but without envying others. She lived in the world of

01:25:52.290 --> 01:25:59.590
wondrous and only riches seemed real to her. Before long she married a rich man and the rings

01:25:59.590 --> 01:26:07.030
and things became visible. I do not know whether the man was the divine selection, but opulence had

01:26:07.030 --> 01:26:15.050
to manifest in her life as she had imaged only opulence. There is no peace or happiness for man

01:26:15.050 --> 01:26:22.270
until he has erased all fear from the subconscious. Fear is misdirected energy and must be redirected.

01:26:22.290 --> 01:26:30.230
Or transmuted into faith. Jesus Christ said, Why are ye fearful, O ye of little faith?

01:26:30.830 --> 01:26:37.630
All things are possible to him that believeth. I am asked so often by my students,

01:26:38.310 --> 01:26:44.890
how can I get rid of fear? I replied by walking up to the thing you are afraid of.

01:26:45.950 --> 01:26:49.430
The lion takes its fierceness from your fear.

01:26:51.050 --> 01:26:56.990
Walk up to the lion and he will disappear. Run away and he runs after you. I have shown

01:26:56.990 --> 01:27:02.150
in previous chapters how the lion of lack disappeared when the individual spent money

01:27:02.150 --> 01:27:09.190
fearlessly, showing faith that God was his supply and therefore unfailing. Many of my

01:27:09.190 --> 01:27:13.730
students have come out of the bondage of poverty and are now bountifully supplied

01:27:13.730 --> 01:27:20.810
through losing all fear of letting money go out. The subconscious is impressed with the truth that

01:27:20.810 --> 01:27:29.550
God is the giver and the gift. Therefore, as one is one with the giver, he is one with the gift.

01:27:30.170 --> 01:27:36.090
A splendid statement is, I now thank God the giver, for God the gift.

01:27:37.050 --> 01:27:44.070
Man has so long separated himself from his good and his supply, through thoughts of separation

01:27:44.070 --> 01:27:50.590
and lack, that sometimes it takes dynamite to dislodge these false ideas from the subconscious,

01:27:51.150 --> 01:27:56.650
and the dynamite is a big situation. We see in the foregoing illustration

01:27:56.650 --> 01:28:02.010
how the individual was freed from his bondage by showing fearlessness.

01:28:03.150 --> 01:28:09.670
Man should watch himself hourly to detect if his motive for action is fear or faith.

01:28:10.730 --> 01:28:19.650
Choose ye this day whom we shall serve, fear or faith. Perhaps one's fear is of personality.

01:28:20.390 --> 01:28:27.050
Then, do not avoid the people feared. Be willing to meet them cheerfully and they will either

01:28:27.690 --> 01:28:33.370
golden links in the chain of one's good, or disappear harmoniously from one's pathway.

01:28:34.470 --> 01:28:41.770
Perhaps one's fear is of disease or germs. Then one should be fearless and undisturbed

01:28:41.770 --> 01:28:50.210
in a germ-laden situation, and he would be immune. One can only contract germs while

01:28:50.210 --> 01:28:57.650
vibrating at the same rate as the germ, and fear drags men down to the level of the germ.

01:28:58.290 --> 01:29:04.570
Of course, the disease-laden germ is the product of carnal mind, as all thought must objectify.

01:29:04.990 --> 01:29:10.070
Germs do not exist in the superconscious or divine mind, therefore are the products of

01:29:10.070 --> 01:29:17.770
man's vain imagination. In the twinkling of an eye, man's release will come when he realizes

01:29:17.770 --> 01:29:25.070
there is no power in evil. The material world will fade away, and the fourth-dimensional world,

01:29:25.270 --> 01:29:29.090
the world of the wondrous, will swing into manifestation.

01:29:30.790 --> 01:29:38.790
And I saw a new heaven and a new earth, and there shall be no more death, neither sorrow nor crying,

01:29:39.510 --> 01:29:45.010
neither shall there be any more pain, for the former things are passed away.

01:30:22.732 --> 01:30:26.632
Every man on this planet is taking his initiation in love.

01:30:27.552 --> 01:30:31.212
A new commandment I give unto you, that ye love one another.

01:30:32.352 --> 01:30:38.552
Ospensky states in Tertium Organum that love is a cosmic phenomenon,

01:30:39.732 --> 01:30:44.972
and opens to man the fourth-dimensional world, the world of the wondrous.

01:30:45.932 --> 01:30:49.392
Real love is selfish and free from fear.

01:30:50.112 --> 01:30:55.952
It pours itself out upon the object of its affection, without demanding any return.

01:30:56.812 --> 01:30:59.292
Its joy is in the joy of giving.

01:31:00.292 --> 01:31:06.112
Love is God in manifestation, and the strongest magnetic force in the universe.

01:31:07.252 --> 01:31:11.372
Pure unselfish love draws to itself its own.

01:31:11.372 --> 01:31:15.432
It does not need to seek or demand.

01:31:17.152 --> 01:31:20.852
Scarcely anyone has the faintest conception of real love.

01:31:21.772 --> 01:31:28.172
Man is selfish, tyrannical, or fearful in his affections, thereby losing the things he loves.

01:31:29.272 --> 01:31:34.212
Jealousy is the worst enemy of love, for the imagination runs riot,

01:31:34.212 --> 01:31:41.832
seeing the loved one attracted to another, and invariably these fears objectify if they are not

01:31:41.832 --> 01:31:49.892
neutralized. For example, a woman came to me in deep distress. The man she loved had left her for

01:31:49.892 --> 01:31:56.712
another woman, and said he never intended to marry her. She was torn with jealousy and resentment,

01:31:57.092 --> 01:32:01.912
and said she hoped he would suffer as he had made her suffer, and added,

01:32:01.912 --> 01:32:09.072
how could he leave me when I loved him so much? I replied, you are not loving that man,

01:32:09.272 --> 01:32:14.772
you are hating him, and added, you can never receive what you have never given.

01:32:15.352 --> 01:32:22.972
Give a perfect love, and you will receive a perfect love. Perfect yourself on this man.

01:32:23.492 --> 01:32:31.812
Give him a perfect unselfish love, demanding nothing in return. Do not criticize or condemn

01:32:31.812 --> 01:32:40.552
and bless him wherever he is. She replied, no, I won't bless him unless I know where he is.

01:32:41.512 --> 01:32:50.012
Well, I said, that is not real love. When you send out real love, real love will return to you,

01:32:50.332 --> 01:32:56.032
either from this man or his equivalent, for if this man is not the divine selection,

01:32:56.032 --> 01:33:02.992
you will not want him. As you are one with God, you are one with the love which belongs to you

01:33:02.992 --> 01:33:10.432
by divine right. Several months passed, and matters remained about the same, but she was

01:33:10.432 --> 01:33:17.432
working conscientiously within herself. I said, when you are no longer disturbed by his cruelty,

01:33:17.772 --> 01:33:23.212
he will cease to be cruel, as you are attracting it through your own emotions.

01:33:24.072 --> 01:33:28.952
Then I told her of a brotherhood in India who never said good morning to each other.

01:33:29.212 --> 01:33:36.872
They used these words, I salute the divinity in you. They saluted the divinity in every man,

01:33:37.212 --> 01:33:42.832
and in the wild animals in the jungle, and they were never harmed, for they saw only God in every

01:33:42.832 --> 01:33:51.432
living thing. I said, salute the divinity in this man, and say, I see your divine self only. I see

01:33:51.812 --> 01:34:01.892
as God sees you, perfect, made in his image and likeness. She found she was becoming more poised

01:34:01.892 --> 01:34:09.052
and gradually losing her resentment. He was a captain, and she always called him the cap.

01:34:10.392 --> 01:34:18.292
One day she said suddenly, God bless the cap wherever he is. I replied, now that is real love,

01:34:18.292 --> 01:34:24.812
and when you have become a complete circle, and are no longer disturbed by the situation,

01:34:25.272 --> 01:34:28.532
you will have his love, or attract its equivalent.

01:34:29.972 --> 01:34:35.332
I was moving at this time, and did not have a telephone, so was out of touch with her for

01:34:35.332 --> 01:34:42.212
a few weeks, when one morning I received a letter saying, we are married. At the earliest

01:34:42.212 --> 01:34:50.092
opportunity I paid her a call. My first words were, what happened? Oh, she exclaimed, a miracle.

01:34:50.672 --> 01:34:57.772
One day I woke up, and all suffering had ceased. I saw him that evening, and he asked me to marry

01:34:57.772 --> 01:35:03.512
him. We were married in about a week, and I have never seen a more devoted man.

01:35:05.712 --> 01:35:10.392
There is an old saying, no man is your enemy, no man is your friend,

01:35:10.952 --> 01:35:17.652
every man is your teacher. So one should become impersonal and learn what each man has to teach

01:35:17.652 --> 01:35:24.732
him, and soon he would learn his lessons and be free. The woman's lover was teaching her selfish

01:35:24.732 --> 01:35:32.112
love, which every man sooner or later must learn. Suffering is not necessary for man's development,

01:35:32.432 --> 01:35:38.592
it is the result of violation of spiritual law, but few people seem able to rouse themselves from

01:35:38.592 --> 01:35:45.272
their soul-sleep without it. When people are happy, they usually become selfish,

01:35:45.712 --> 01:35:52.432
and automatically the law of karma is set in action. Man often suffers loss through

01:35:52.432 --> 01:35:58.832
lack of appreciation. I knew a woman who had a very nice husband, but she said often,

01:35:59.212 --> 01:36:03.532
I don't care anything about being married, but that is nothing against my husband,

01:36:03.532 --> 01:36:10.632
I'm simply not interested in married life. She had other interests, and scarcely remembered she

01:36:10.632 --> 01:36:18.272
had a husband, she only thought of him when she saw him. One day her husband told her he was in

01:36:18.272 --> 01:36:25.072
love with another woman, and left. She came to me in distress and resentment. I replied,

01:36:25.752 --> 01:36:30.672
it is exactly what you spoke the word for, you said you didn't care anything about being married,

01:36:30.672 --> 01:36:38.212
so the subconscious worked to get you unmarried. She said, oh yes, I see, people get what they want,

01:36:38.412 --> 01:36:44.112
and then feel very much hurt. She soon became in perfect harmony with the situation,

01:36:44.512 --> 01:36:50.872
and knew they were both much happier apart. When a woman becomes indifferent or critical,

01:36:51.152 --> 01:36:57.212
and ceases to be an inspiration to her husband, he misses the stimulus of their early relationship,

01:36:57.212 --> 01:37:03.852
and is restless and unhappy. A man came to me dejected, miserable, and poor.

01:37:04.532 --> 01:37:10.652
His wife was interested in the science of numbers, and had had him read. It seems the

01:37:10.652 --> 01:37:16.392
report was not very favorable, for he said, my wife says I'll never amount to anything because

01:37:16.392 --> 01:37:23.452
I am a two. I replied, I don't care what your number is, you are a perfect idea in divine mind,

01:37:23.452 --> 01:37:29.932
and we will demand the success and prosperity which are already planned for you by that

01:37:29.932 --> 01:37:37.612
infinite intelligence. Within a few weeks he had a very fine position, and a year or two later

01:37:37.612 --> 01:37:44.772
he achieved a brilliant success as a writer. No man is a success in business unless he loves his

01:37:44.772 --> 01:37:52.832
work. The picture the artist paints for love of his art is his greatest work. The potboiler

01:37:52.832 --> 01:37:59.732
is always something to live down. No man can attract money if he despises it.

01:38:00.332 --> 01:38:06.112
Many people are kept in poverty by saying, money means nothing to me, I have a contempt

01:38:06.112 --> 01:38:12.932
for people who have it. This is the reason so many artists are poor. Their contempt for money

01:38:12.932 --> 01:38:19.172
separates them from it. I remember hearing one artist say of another, he's no good as an artist,

01:38:19.172 --> 01:38:25.392
but he has money in the bank. This attitude of mind, of course, separates man from his supply.

01:38:26.092 --> 01:38:32.132
He must be in harmony with a thing in order to attract it. Money is God in manifestation,

01:38:32.552 --> 01:38:40.352
as freedom from want and limitation, but it must be always kept in circulation and put to right

01:38:40.352 --> 01:38:48.712
uses. Hoarding and saving react with grim vengeance. This does not mean that man should not have houses

01:38:48.712 --> 01:38:56.932
and lots, stocks and bonds, for the barns of the righteous man shall be full. It means that man

01:38:56.932 --> 01:39:04.432
should not hoard even the principal if an occasion arises when money is necessary. In letting it go

01:39:04.432 --> 01:39:12.292
out fearlessly and cheerfully, he opens the way for more to come in, for God is man's unfailing

01:39:12.292 --> 01:39:19.712
and inexhaustible supply. This is the spiritual attitude towards money, and the great bank of

01:39:19.712 --> 01:39:27.252
the universal never fails. We see an example of hoarding in the film production of Greed.

01:39:28.172 --> 01:39:34.932
The woman won $5,000 in a lottery, but would not spend it. She hoarded and saved,

01:39:35.492 --> 01:39:41.092
let her husband suffer and starve, and eventually she scrubbed floors for a living.

01:39:41.812 --> 01:39:48.012
She loved the money itself and put it above everything, and one night she was murdered

01:39:48.012 --> 01:39:55.052
and the money taken from her. This is an example of where love of money is the root of all evil.

01:39:56.272 --> 01:40:03.192
Money in itself is good and beneficial, but used for destructive purposes, hoarded and saved,

01:40:03.612 --> 01:40:09.732
or considered more important than love, brings disease and disaster and the loss of the money

01:40:09.732 --> 01:40:18.672
itself. Follow the path of love, and all things are added, for God is love and God is supply.

01:40:19.692 --> 01:40:26.512
Follow the path of selfishness and greed, and the supply vanishes, or man is separated from it.

01:40:27.272 --> 01:40:34.352
For example, I knew the case of a very rich woman who hoarded her income. She rarely gave anything

01:40:34.352 --> 01:40:41.332
away, but bought and bought and bought things for herself. She was very fond of necklaces,

01:40:41.632 --> 01:40:45.772
and a friend once asked her how many she possessed. She replied,

01:40:46.152 --> 01:40:53.612
Sixty-seven. She bought them and put them away, carefully wrapped in tissue paper. Had she used

01:40:53.612 --> 01:41:00.712
the necklaces, it would have been quite legitimate, but she was violating the law of use. Her closets

01:41:00.712 --> 01:41:07.212
were filled with clothes she never wore, and jewels which never saw the light. The old woman's arms

01:41:07.212 --> 01:41:12.612
were gradually becoming paralyzed from holding on to things, and eventually she was considered

01:41:12.612 --> 01:41:18.432
incapable of looking after her affairs, and her wealth was handed over to others to manage.

01:41:19.552 --> 01:41:28.232
So man, in ignorance of the law, brings about his own destruction. All disease, all unhappiness,

01:41:28.232 --> 01:41:35.772
come from the violation of the law of love. Man's boomerangs of hate, resentment, and criticism

01:41:35.772 --> 01:41:43.532
come back laden with sickness and sorrow. Love seems almost a lost art, but the man with the

01:41:43.532 --> 01:41:51.032
knowledge of spiritual law knows it must be regained, for without it he has become as sounding

01:41:51.032 --> 01:41:59.372
brass and tinkling cymbals. For example, I had a student who came to me month after month to

01:41:59.372 --> 01:42:05.552
clean her consciousness of resentment. After a while she arrived at the point where she

01:42:05.552 --> 01:42:13.532
resented only one woman, but that one woman kept her busy. Little by little she became poised and

01:42:13.532 --> 01:42:21.252
harmonious, and one day all resentment was wiped out. She came in radiant and exclaimed,

01:42:21.732 --> 01:42:28.112
You can't understand how I feel. The woman said something to me, and instead of being furious,

01:42:28.572 --> 01:42:37.672
I was loving and kind. And she apologized and was perfectly lovely to me. No one can understand the

01:42:37.672 --> 01:42:45.312
lightness I feel within. Love and goodwill are invaluable in business. For example,

01:42:45.792 --> 01:42:51.852
a woman came to me complaining of her employer. She said she was cold and critical,

01:42:52.112 --> 01:42:59.932
and she knew she did not want her in the position. Well, I replied, salute the divinity in the woman

01:42:59.932 --> 01:43:08.992
and send her love. She said, I can't. She's a marble woman. I answered, You remember the story

01:43:08.992 --> 01:43:16.032
of the sculptor who asked for a certain piece of marble? He was asked why he wanted it, and he

01:43:16.032 --> 01:43:23.672
replied, because there is an angel in the marble. And out of it he produced a wonderful work of art.

01:43:24.452 --> 01:43:30.732
She said, Very well, I'll try it. A week later she came back and said,

01:43:30.972 --> 01:43:36.632
I did what you told me, and now the woman is very kind and took me out in her car.

01:43:40.792 --> 01:43:46.952
People are sometimes filled with remorse for having done someone an unkindness, perhaps years

01:43:46.952 --> 01:43:54.852
ago. If the wrong cannot be righted, its effect can be neutralized by doing someone a kindness

01:43:54.852 --> 01:44:03.232
in the present. This one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind and reaching forth

01:44:03.232 --> 01:44:10.792
unto those things which are before. Sorrow, regret, and remorse tear down the cells of the body

01:44:10.792 --> 01:44:17.192
and poison the atmosphere of the individual. A woman said to me in deep sorrow,

01:44:17.792 --> 01:44:23.492
treat me to be happy and joyous, for my sorrow makes me so irritable with the members of my family

01:44:23.492 --> 01:44:29.952
that I keep making more karma. I was asked to treat a woman who was mourning for her daughter.

01:44:30.612 --> 01:44:35.792
I denied all belief in loss and separation and affirmed that God was the woman's joy,

01:44:35.792 --> 01:44:42.392
love, and peace. The woman gained her poise at once, but sent word by her son

01:44:42.392 --> 01:44:48.032
not to treat any longer, because she was so happy it wasn't respectable.

01:44:49.812 --> 01:44:58.312
So mortal mind loves to hang on to its griefs and regrets. I knew a woman who went about bragging

01:44:58.312 --> 01:45:04.672
of her troubles, so of course she always had something to brag about. The old idea was,

01:45:04.672 --> 01:45:11.832
if a woman did not worry about her children, she was not a good mother. Now we know that mother

01:45:11.832 --> 01:45:17.432
fear is responsible for many of the diseases and accidents which come into the lives of children,

01:45:17.932 --> 01:45:24.612
for fear pictures vividly the disease or situation feared, and these pictures objectify if not

01:45:24.612 --> 01:45:31.572
neutralized. Happy is the mother who can say sincerely that she puts her child in God's hands

01:45:31.572 --> 01:45:34.672
and therefore knows that he is divinely protected.

01:45:37.552 --> 01:45:43.532
For example, a woman awoke suddenly in the night, feeling her brother was in great danger.

01:45:44.032 --> 01:45:49.432
Instead of giving in to her fears, she commenced making statements of truth, saying,

01:45:49.972 --> 01:45:56.532
Man is a perfect idea in divine mind and is always in his right place. Therefore,

01:45:56.532 --> 01:46:03.912
my brother is in his right place and is divinely protected. The next day she found that her brother

01:46:03.912 --> 01:46:09.892
had been in close proximity to an explosion in a mine, but had miraculously escaped.

01:46:10.992 --> 01:46:17.472
So man is his brother's keeper in thought, and every man should know that the thing he loves

01:46:17.472 --> 01:46:24.092
dwells in the secret place of the Most High and abides under the shadow of the Almighty.

01:46:25.052 --> 01:46:31.572
There shall no evil befall thee, neither shall any plague come nigh thy dwelling.

01:46:32.532 --> 01:46:38.552
Perfect love casteth out fear, he that feareth is not made perfect in love,

01:46:38.952 --> 01:46:42.552
and love is the fulfilling of the law.

01:47:12.395 --> 01:47:16.275
VIII. INTUITION OR GUIDANCE.

01:47:16.275 --> 01:47:22.495
In all thy ways acknowledge him, and he shall direct thy paths.

01:47:23.795 --> 01:47:29.735
There is nothing too great of accomplishment for the man who knows the power of his word,

01:47:29.975 --> 01:47:36.735
and who follows his intuitive leads. By the word he starts in action unseen forces,

01:47:37.115 --> 01:47:44.995
and can rebuild his body or remould his affairs. It is therefore of the utmost importance to choose

01:47:44.995 --> 01:47:50.615
the right words, and the student carefully selects the affirmation he wishes to catapult

01:47:50.615 --> 01:47:58.155
into the invisible. He knows that God is his supply, and that there is a supply for every demand,

01:47:58.535 --> 01:48:04.695
and that his spoken word releases this supply. Ask, and ye shall receive.

01:48:05.995 --> 01:48:12.775
Man must make the first move. Draw nigh to God, and he will draw nigh to you.

01:48:13.575 --> 01:48:19.235
I have often been asked just how to make a demonstration. I reply,

01:48:19.835 --> 01:48:27.135
Speak the word, and then do not do anything until you get a definite lead. Demand the lead, saying,

01:48:27.755 --> 01:48:33.455
Infinite spirit, reveal to me the way, let me know if there's anything for me to do.

01:48:34.515 --> 01:48:39.895
The answer will come through intuition, or hunch, a chance remark from someone,

01:48:39.895 --> 01:48:47.915
or a passage in a book, etc. etc. The answers are sometimes quite startling in their exactness.

01:48:48.095 --> 01:48:54.495
For example, a woman desired a large sum of money. She spoke the words, Infinite spirit,

01:48:54.855 --> 01:49:01.315
open the way for my immediate supply, let all that is mine by divine right now reach me in

01:49:01.315 --> 01:49:08.155
great avalanches of abundance. Then she added, Give me a definite lead, let me know if there

01:49:08.155 --> 01:49:14.875
is anything for me to do. The thought came quickly. Give a certain friend, who had helped

01:49:14.875 --> 01:49:21.315
her spiritually, a hundred dollars. She told her friend, who said, Wait and get another lead

01:49:21.315 --> 01:49:28.375
before giving it. So she waited, and that day met a woman who said to her, I gave someone a dollar

01:49:28.375 --> 01:49:36.635
today. It was just as much for me as it would be for you to give someone a hundred. This was indeed

01:49:36.635 --> 01:49:43.415
an unmistakable lead, so she knew she was right in giving the hundred dollars. It was a gift which

01:49:43.415 --> 01:49:49.255
proved a great investment for shortly after that, a large sum of money came to her in a remarkable

01:49:49.255 --> 01:49:57.415
way. Giving opens the way for receiving. In order to create activity in finances, one should give.

01:49:58.235 --> 01:50:05.415
Tithing, or giving one tenth of one's income, is an old Jewish custom and is sure to bring increase.

01:50:06.215 --> 01:50:12.515
Many of the richest men in the country have been tithers and have never known it to fail as an

01:50:12.515 --> 01:50:19.975
investment. The tenth part goes forth and returns blessed and multiplied, but the gift or tithe must

01:50:19.975 --> 01:50:27.275
be given with love and cheerfulness, for God loveth a cheerful giver. Bills should be paid

01:50:27.275 --> 01:50:33.635
cheerfully. All money should be sent forth fearlessly and with a blessing. This attitude

01:50:33.635 --> 01:50:42.355
of mind makes man master of money. It is his to obey, and his spoken word then opens vast reservoirs

01:50:42.355 --> 01:50:50.575
of wealth. Man himself limits his supply by his limited vision. Sometimes the student has a great

01:50:50.575 --> 01:50:57.315
realization of wealth, but is afraid to act. The vision and action must go hand in hand,

01:50:57.315 --> 01:51:00.675
as in the case of the man who bought the fur-lined overcoat.

01:51:01.755 --> 01:51:08.075
A woman came to me asking me to speak the word for a position, so I demanded,

01:51:08.655 --> 01:51:16.935
Infinite Spirit, open the way for this woman's right position. Never ask for just a position.

01:51:17.475 --> 01:51:24.695
Ask for the right position, the place already planned in divine mind, as it is the only one

01:51:24.695 --> 01:51:31.595
will give satisfaction. I then gave thanks that she had already received, and that it would

01:51:31.595 --> 01:51:38.675
manifest quickly. Very soon she had three positions offered her, two in New York and

01:51:38.675 --> 01:51:45.915
one in Palm Beach, and she did not know which one to choose. I said, ask for a definite lead.

01:51:46.995 --> 01:51:52.155
The time was almost up and was still undecided when one day she telephoned,

01:51:52.155 --> 01:51:59.675
When I woke up this morning I could smell Palm Beach. She had been there before and knew its

01:51:59.675 --> 01:52:06.135
balmy fragrance. I replied, well if you can smell Palm Beach from here, it's certainly your lead.

01:52:07.215 --> 01:52:13.575
She accepted the position and it proved a great success. Often one's lead comes at an unexpected

01:52:13.575 --> 01:52:20.895
time. One day I was walking down the street when suddenly I felt a strong urge to go to a certain

01:52:20.895 --> 01:52:27.315
bakery a block or two away. The reasoning mind resisted, arguing, there is nothing there that

01:52:27.315 --> 01:52:34.775
you want. However, I had learned not to reason, so I went to the bakery, looked at everything,

01:52:34.995 --> 01:52:40.635
and there was certainly nothing there that I wanted. But coming out, I encountered a woman

01:52:40.635 --> 01:52:45.435
I had thought of often, and who was in great need of the help which I could give her.

01:52:45.435 --> 01:52:50.175
So often, one goes for one thing and finds another.

01:52:51.955 --> 01:52:59.735
Intuition is a spiritual faculty and does not explain, but simply points the way. A person

01:52:59.735 --> 01:53:07.975
often receives a lead during a treatment. The idea that comes may seem quite irrelevant, but

01:53:07.975 --> 01:53:11.275
some of God's leadings are mysterious.

01:53:13.255 --> 01:53:19.555
In the class one day, I was treating that each individual would receive a definite lead.

01:53:20.275 --> 01:53:24.095
A woman came to me afterwards and said, while you were treating,

01:53:24.255 --> 01:53:27.775
I got the hunch to take my furniture out of storage and get an apartment.

01:53:28.775 --> 01:53:34.275
The woman had come to be treated for health. I told her I knew in getting a home of her own,

01:53:34.275 --> 01:53:39.795
her health would improve, and I added, I believe your trouble, which is a congestion,

01:53:40.215 --> 01:53:47.035
has come from having things stored away. Congestion of things causes congestion in the body.

01:53:47.755 --> 01:53:51.895
You have violated the law of use, and your body is paying the penalty.

01:53:52.855 --> 01:53:59.375
So I gave thanks that divine order was established in her mind, body and affairs.

01:54:00.155 --> 01:54:06.495
People little dream of how their affairs react on the body. There is a mental correspondence

01:54:06.495 --> 01:54:12.515
for every disease. A person might receive instantaneous healing through the realization

01:54:12.515 --> 01:54:18.815
of his body being a perfect idea in divine mind and therefore whole and perfect, but if he

01:54:18.815 --> 01:54:26.955
continues his destructive thinking, hoarding, hating, fearing, condemning, the disease will return.

01:54:27.775 --> 01:54:35.255
Jesus Christ knew that all sickness came from sin, but admonished the leper after the healing

01:54:35.775 --> 01:54:44.195
to go and sin no more, lest a worse thing come upon him. So man's soul, or subconscious mind,

01:54:44.735 --> 01:54:52.515
must be washed whiter than snow for permanent healing, and the metaphysician is always delving

01:54:52.515 --> 01:55:01.455
deep for the correspondence. Jesus Christ said, condemn not, lest ye also be condemned.

01:55:02.815 --> 01:55:11.035
Judge not, lest ye be judged. Many people have attracted disease and unhappiness through the

01:55:11.035 --> 01:55:20.015
condemnation of others. What man condemns in others, he attracts to himself. For example,

01:55:20.015 --> 01:55:26.455
a friend came to me in anger and distress because her husband had deserted her for another woman.

01:55:27.215 --> 01:55:30.215
She condemned the other woman and said continually,

01:55:30.955 --> 01:55:35.895
she knew he was a married man, she had no right to accept his attentions.

01:55:37.035 --> 01:55:43.895
I replied, stop condemning the woman, bless her, and be through with the situation, otherwise you

01:55:43.895 --> 01:55:50.655
are attracting the same thing to yourself. She was deaf to my words, and a year or two later

01:55:50.655 --> 01:55:58.655
became deeply interested in a married man herself. Man picks up a live wire whenever he criticizes

01:55:58.655 --> 01:56:07.315
or condemns, and may expect a shock. Indecision is a stumbling block in many a pathway. In order

01:56:07.315 --> 01:56:15.175
to overcome it, make the statement repeatedly, I am always under direct inspiration. I make

01:56:15.175 --> 01:56:22.915
right decisions quickly. These words impress the subconscious, and soon one finds himself

01:56:22.915 --> 01:56:30.275
awake and alert, making his right moves without hesitation. I have found it destructive to look

01:56:30.275 --> 01:56:37.695
the psychic plane for guidance, as it is the plane of many minds, and not the one mind.

01:56:38.475 --> 01:56:44.815
As man opens his mind to subjectivity, he becomes a target for destructive forces.

01:56:45.335 --> 01:56:52.895
The psychic plane is the result of man's mortal thought, and is on the plane of opposites. He may

01:56:52.895 --> 01:57:00.955
receive either good or bad messages. The science of numbers and the reading of horoscopes keep man

01:57:00.955 --> 01:57:09.035
down the mental or mortal plane, for they deal only with the karmic path. I know of a man who

01:57:09.035 --> 01:57:15.835
should have been dead years ago according to his horoscope, but he is alive and a leader of one of

01:57:15.835 --> 01:57:23.615
the biggest movements in this country for the uplift of humanity. It takes a very strong mind

01:57:23.615 --> 01:57:28.295
to neutralize a prophecy of evil. The student should declare,

01:57:29.115 --> 01:57:36.315
Every false prophecy shall come to naught. Every plan my Father in heaven has not planned

01:57:36.315 --> 01:57:45.635
shall be dissolved and dissipated. The divine idea now comes to pass. However, if any good message

01:57:45.635 --> 01:57:53.675
has ever been given one of coming happiness or wealth, harbor and expect it, and it will manifest

01:57:53.675 --> 01:58:01.275
sooner or later through the law of expectancy. Man's will should be used to back the universal will.

01:58:01.855 --> 01:58:09.255
I will that the will of God be done. It is God's will to give every man

01:58:09.255 --> 01:58:15.315
every righteous desire of his heart, and man's will should be used to hold the perfect vision.

01:58:15.315 --> 01:58:22.735
Without wavering, the prodigal son said, I will arise and go to my Father.

01:58:24.115 --> 01:58:29.695
It is indeed often an effort of the will to leave the husks and swine of mortal thinking.

01:58:30.335 --> 01:58:37.715
It is so much easier for the average person to have fear than faith. So faith is an effort of the

01:58:37.715 --> 01:58:38.015
will.

01:58:39.035 --> 01:58:45.495
As man becomes spiritually awakened, he recognizes that any external inharmony is

01:58:45.495 --> 01:58:52.355
the correspondence of mental inharmony. If he stumbles or falls, he may know he is stumbling

01:58:52.355 --> 01:58:59.335
or falling in consciousness. One day a student was walking along the street, condemning someone

01:58:59.335 --> 01:59:05.735
in her thoughts. She was saying mentally, that woman is the most disagreeable woman on earth.

01:59:05.735 --> 01:59:13.455
When suddenly three boy scouts rushed around the corner and almost knocked her over, she did not

01:59:13.455 --> 01:59:19.675
condemn the boy scouts, but immediately called on the law of forgiveness and saluted the divinity

01:59:19.675 --> 01:59:27.095
in the woman. Wisdom's ways are ways of pleasantness, and all her paths are peace.

01:59:28.115 --> 01:59:33.915
When one has made his demands upon the universal, he must be ready for surprises.

01:59:34.635 --> 01:59:40.795
Everything may seem to be going wrong, when in reality it is going right. For example,

01:59:41.215 --> 01:59:47.835
a woman was told that there was no loss in divine mind, therefore she could not lose anything which

01:59:47.835 --> 01:59:56.355
belonged to her. Anything lost would be returned, or she would receive its equivalent. Several years

01:59:56.355 --> 02:00:03.135
previously she had lost $2,000. She had loaned the money to a relative during her lifetime,

02:00:03.135 --> 02:00:10.655
but the relative had died, leaving no mention of it in her will. The woman was resentful and angry,

02:00:11.055 --> 02:00:16.235
and as she had no written statement of the transaction, she never received the money,

02:00:16.575 --> 02:00:23.095
so she determined to deny the loss and collect the $2,000 from the bank of the universal.

02:00:23.895 --> 02:00:30.255
She had to begin by forgiving the woman, as resentment and unforgiveness closed the door

02:00:30.255 --> 02:00:37.395
of this wonderful bank. She made this statement, I deny loss, there is no loss in divine mind,

02:00:37.595 --> 02:00:45.775
therefore I cannot lose the $2,000 which belonged to me by divine right. As one door shuts, another

02:00:45.775 --> 02:00:53.135
opens. She was living in an apartment house, which was for sale, and in the lease was a clause,

02:00:53.575 --> 02:00:58.615
stating that if the house was sold, the tenants would be required to move out within 90 days.

02:00:59.255 --> 02:01:06.175
Suddenly the landlord broke the leases and raised the rent. Again injustice was on her pathway,

02:01:06.535 --> 02:01:10.955
but this time she was undisturbed. She blessed the landlord and said,

02:01:11.455 --> 02:01:17.435
as the rent has been raised, it means that I'll be that much richer, for God is my supply.

02:01:19.735 --> 02:01:26.475
The new leases were made out for the advanced rent, but by some divine mistake the 90-day

02:01:26.475 --> 02:01:32.735
clause had been forgotten. Soon after, the landlord had an opportunity to sell the house.

02:01:33.235 --> 02:01:38.395
On account of the mistake in the new leases, the tenants held possession for another year.

02:01:39.295 --> 02:01:45.455
The agent offered each tenant $200 if he would vacate. Several families moved,

02:01:46.115 --> 02:01:52.475
three remained, including the woman. A month or two passed, and the agent again appeared.

02:01:52.475 --> 02:01:57.395
This time he said to the woman, will you break your lease for the sum of $1,500?

02:01:58.495 --> 02:02:05.255
It flashed upon her, here comes the $2,000. She remembered having said to friends in the house,

02:02:06.095 --> 02:02:11.755
we will all act together if anything more is said about leaving. So her lead was to consult her

02:02:11.755 --> 02:02:18.695
friends. These friends said, well, if they have offered you $1,500, they will certainly give $2,000.

02:02:19.325 --> 02:02:25.355
So she received a check for $2,000 for giving up the apartment. It was certainly a remarkable

02:02:25.355 --> 02:02:31.355
working of the law, and the apparent injustice was merely an opening for the way for her

02:02:31.355 --> 02:02:40.855
demonstration. It proved that there is no loss, and when man takes his spiritual stand,

02:02:41.355 --> 02:02:45.655
he collects all that is his from this great reservoir of good.

02:02:47.555 --> 02:02:51.835
I will restore to you the years the locusts have eaten.

02:02:52.715 --> 02:02:59.575
The locusts are the doubts, fears, resentments, and regrets of mortal thinking. These adverse

02:02:59.575 --> 02:03:07.615
thoughts alone rob man, for no man gives to himself but himself, and no man takes away from

02:03:07.615 --> 02:03:15.275
himself but himself. Man is here to prove God and to bear witness to the truth,

02:03:15.915 --> 02:03:22.555
and he can only prove God by bringing plenty out of lack and justice out of injustice.

02:03:23.715 --> 02:03:31.415
Prove me now herewith, saith the Lord of hosts, if I will not open you the windows of heaven

02:03:31.415 --> 02:03:36.355
and pour out a blessing, that there shall be not room enough to receive it.

02:04:08.132 --> 02:04:13.112
Perfect Self-Expression or The Divine Design.

02:04:15.392 --> 02:04:21.372
No wind can drive my bark astray, nor change the tide of destiny.

02:04:22.712 --> 02:04:28.792
There is for each man perfect self-expression. There is a place which he is to fill,

02:04:29.192 --> 02:04:36.392
and no one else can fill. Something which he is to do, which no one else can do. It is his destiny.

02:04:37.252 --> 02:04:43.872
This achievement is held, a perfect idea in divine mind, awaiting man's recognition.

02:04:44.632 --> 02:04:51.212
As the imaging faculty is the creative faculty, it is necessary for man to see the idea before

02:04:51.212 --> 02:04:57.872
it can manifest. So man's highest demand is for the divine design of his life.

02:04:58.712 --> 02:05:05.052
He may not have the faintest conception of what it is, for there is possibly some marvelous talent

02:05:05.052 --> 02:05:08.862
hidden deep within him. His demand should be,

02:05:09.792 --> 02:05:14.812
Infinite Spirit, open the way for the divine design of my life to manifest.

02:05:15.452 --> 02:05:22.532
Let the genius within me now be released. Let me see clearly the perfect plan.

02:05:23.612 --> 02:05:29.712
The perfect plan includes health, wealth, love, and perfect self-expression.

02:05:29.712 --> 02:05:37.072
This is the square of life, which brings perfect happiness. When one has made this demand,

02:05:37.352 --> 02:05:43.892
he may find great changes taking place in his life, for nearly every man has wandered far from

02:05:43.892 --> 02:05:51.692
the divine design. I know, in one woman's case, it was as though a cyclone had struck her affairs,

02:05:52.192 --> 02:05:58.712
but readjustments came quickly, and new and wonderful conditions took the place of old ones.

02:05:59.612 --> 02:06:05.512
Perfect self-expression will never be labor, but of such absorbing interest that it will seem

02:06:05.512 --> 02:06:12.012
almost like play. The student knows also, as man comes into the world financed by God,

02:06:12.512 --> 02:06:16.792
the supply needed for his perfect self-expression will be at hand.

02:06:18.192 --> 02:06:24.252
Many a genius has struggled for years with the problem of supply, when his spoken word and faith

02:06:24.252 --> 02:06:31.132
would have released quickly the necessary funds. For example, after the class one day,

02:06:31.252 --> 02:06:39.112
a man came to me and handed me a cent. He said, I have just seven cents in the world and I'm going

02:06:39.112 --> 02:06:46.192
to give you one, for I have faith in the power of your spoken word. I want you to speak the word

02:06:46.192 --> 02:06:53.892
for my perfect self-expression and prosperity. I spoke the word and did not see him again until

02:06:53.892 --> 02:07:01.472
a year later. He came in one day, successful and happy, with a roll of yellow bills in a pocket.

02:07:02.272 --> 02:07:08.232
He said, immediately after you spoke the word, I had a position offered me in a distant city,

02:07:08.572 --> 02:07:12.212
and am now demonstrating health, happiness, and supply.

02:07:13.452 --> 02:07:20.852
A woman's self-expression may be in becoming a perfect wife, a perfect mother, a perfect homemaker,

02:07:20.852 --> 02:07:28.772
and not necessarily in having a public career. Demand definite leads, and the way will be made

02:07:28.772 --> 02:07:37.752
easy and successful. One should not visualize or force a mental picture. When he demands the divine

02:07:37.752 --> 02:07:44.832
design to come into his conscious mind, he will receive flashes of inspiration and begin to see

02:07:44.832 --> 02:07:51.092
himself making some great accomplishment. This is the picture or idea he must hold without

02:07:51.092 --> 02:07:58.312
wavering. The thing man seeks is seeking him. The telephone was seeking Bell.

02:07:59.772 --> 02:08:06.132
Parents should never force careers and professions upon their children. With a knowledge of spiritual

02:08:06.132 --> 02:08:13.752
truth, the divine plan could be spoken for early in childhood or prenatally. A prenatal treatment

02:08:13.752 --> 02:08:21.412
should be, let the God in this child have perfect self-expression. Let the divine design of his

02:08:21.412 --> 02:08:27.372
mind, body, and affairs be made manifest throughout his life, throughout eternity.

02:08:28.732 --> 02:08:36.872
God's will be done, not man's. God's pattern, not man's pattern, is the command we find running

02:08:36.872 --> 02:08:42.872
through all the scriptures, and the Bible is a book dealing with the science of the mind.

02:08:42.872 --> 02:08:49.392
It is a book telling man how to release his soul or subconscious mind from bondage.

02:08:50.172 --> 02:08:55.032
The battles described are pictures of man waging war against mortal thoughts.

02:08:55.852 --> 02:09:02.212
A man's foes shall be they of his own household. Every man is Jehoshaphat,

02:09:02.672 --> 02:09:08.892
and every man is David, who slays Goliath, mortal thinking, with the little white stone,

02:09:08.892 --> 02:09:15.432
faith. So man must be careful that he is not the wicked and slothful servant

02:09:15.432 --> 02:09:22.292
who buried his talent. There is a terrible penalty to be paid for not using one's ability.

02:09:23.432 --> 02:09:30.532
Often, fear stands between man and his perfect self-expression. Stage fright has hampered many

02:09:30.532 --> 02:09:37.972
a genius. This may be overcome by the spoken word or treatment. The individual then loses

02:09:37.972 --> 02:09:44.172
all self-consciousness and feels simply that he is a channel for infinite intelligence to

02:09:44.172 --> 02:09:51.772
express itself through. He is under direct inspiration, fearless and confident, for he

02:09:51.772 --> 02:09:58.672
feels that it is the Father within who does the work. A young boy came often to my class

02:09:58.672 --> 02:10:04.172
with his mother. He asked me to speak the word for his coming examinations at school.

02:10:04.172 --> 02:10:11.412
I told him to make the statement, I am one with infinite intelligence. I know everything

02:10:11.412 --> 02:10:17.612
I should know on this subject. He had an excellent knowledge of history but was not sure of his

02:10:17.612 --> 02:10:23.712
arithmetic. I saw him afterwards and he said, I spoke the word for my arithmetic and passed

02:10:23.712 --> 02:10:29.732
with the highest honors, but I thought I could depend upon myself for history and got a very

02:10:29.732 --> 02:10:37.032
poor mark. Man often receives a setback when he is too sure of himself, which means he is trusting

02:10:37.032 --> 02:10:44.612
to his personality and not the Father within. Another of my students gave me an example of this.

02:10:45.032 --> 02:10:51.132
She took an extended trip abroad one summer, visiting many countries, where she was ignorant

02:10:51.132 --> 02:10:57.492
of the languages. She was calling for guidance and protection every minute and her affairs went

02:10:57.492 --> 02:11:04.512
smoothly and miraculously. Her luggage was never delayed nor lost. Accommodations were always ready

02:11:04.512 --> 02:11:11.312
for her at the best hotels and she had perfect service wherever she went. She returned to New

02:11:11.312 --> 02:11:17.712
York. Knowing the language, she felt God was no longer necessary, so looked after her affairs in

02:11:17.712 --> 02:11:25.212
an ordinary manner. Everything went wrong. Her trunks delayed amid inharmony and confusion.

02:11:26.092 --> 02:11:33.372
The student must form the habit of practicing the presence of God every minute, in all thy ways

02:11:33.372 --> 02:11:41.632
acknowledge him. Nothing is too small or too great. Sometimes an insignificant incident may be the

02:11:41.632 --> 02:11:47.932
turning point in a man's life. Robert Fulton, watching some boiling water simmering in a tea

02:11:47.932 --> 02:11:56.612
saw a steamboat. I have seen a student often keep back his demonstration through resistance

02:11:56.612 --> 02:12:03.612
or pointing the way. He pins his faith to one channel only and dictates just the way he desires

02:12:03.612 --> 02:12:11.612
the manifestation to come, which brings things to a standstill. My way, not your way, is the command

02:12:11.612 --> 02:12:19.332
of infinite intelligence. Like all power, be it steam or electricity, it must have a non-resistant

02:12:19.332 --> 02:12:26.072
engine or instrument to work through, and man is that engine or instrument. Over and over again,

02:12:26.252 --> 02:12:35.272
man is told to stand still. Oh, Judah, fear not, but tomorrow go out against them, for the Lord

02:12:35.272 --> 02:12:42.392
will be with you. You shall not need to fight this battle. Set yourselves, stand ye still,

02:12:42.612 --> 02:12:51.372
and see the salvation of the Lord with you. We see this in the incidents of the $2,000 coming

02:12:51.372 --> 02:12:57.332
to the woman through the landlord when she became non-resistant and undisturbed, and the woman who

02:12:57.332 --> 02:13:05.772
the man's love after all suffering had ceased. The student's goal is poise. Poise is power,

02:13:06.192 --> 02:13:13.772
for it gives God-power a chance to rush through man, to will and to do its good pleasure.

02:13:14.832 --> 02:13:21.392
Poised, he thinks clearly and makes right decisions quickly. He never misses a trick.

02:13:22.592 --> 02:13:28.992
Anger blurs the visions, poisons the blood, is the root of many diseases, and causes wrong

02:13:28.992 --> 02:13:36.412
decisions leading to failure. It has been named one of the worst sins, as its reaction is so

02:13:36.412 --> 02:13:43.232
harmful. The student learns that in metaphysics, sin has a much broader meaning than in the old

02:13:43.232 --> 02:13:51.872
teaching. Whatsoever is not of faith is sin. He finds that fear and worry are deadly sins.

02:13:52.292 --> 02:13:58.692
They are inverted faith, and through distorted mental pictures bring to pass the thing he fears.

02:13:59.392 --> 02:14:06.592
His work is to drive out these enemies from the subconscious mind. When man is fearless,

02:14:06.592 --> 02:14:12.652
he is finished. Man is God afraid.

02:14:14.692 --> 02:14:21.192
So as we read in the previous chapters, man can only vanquish fear by walking up to the

02:14:21.192 --> 02:14:27.932
thing he is afraid of. When Jehoshaphat and his army prepared to meet the enemy, singing,

02:14:28.552 --> 02:14:34.572
Praise the Lord, for his mercy endureth forever, they found their enemies had destroyed each other,

02:14:34.572 --> 02:14:41.252
and there was nothing to fight. For example, a woman asked a friend to deliver a message

02:14:41.252 --> 02:14:46.832
to another friend. The woman feared to give the message as the reasoning mind said,

02:14:47.392 --> 02:14:53.652
don't get mixed up in this affair, don't give that message. She was troubled in spirit,

02:14:53.872 --> 02:15:00.632
for she had given her promise. At last she determined to walk up to the lion and call

02:15:00.632 --> 02:15:06.392
the law of divine protection. She met the friend to whom she was to deliver the message.

02:15:06.832 --> 02:15:11.892
She opened her mouth to speak it when her friend said, so and so has left town.

02:15:13.052 --> 02:15:19.272
This made it unnecessary to give the message, as a situation depended upon the person being in town.

02:15:19.932 --> 02:15:27.132
As she was willing to do it, she was not obliged to, as she did not fear. The situation vanished.

02:15:28.192 --> 02:15:35.192
The student often delays his demonstration through a belief in incompletion. He should make this

02:15:35.192 --> 02:15:43.832
statement, in divine mind there is only completion, therefore my demonstration is completed,

02:15:44.592 --> 02:15:52.852
my perfect word, my perfect home, my perfect health. Whatever he demands are perfect ideas

02:15:52.852 --> 02:15:58.312
registered in divine mind and must manifest under grace in a perfect way.

02:15:59.232 --> 02:16:05.932
He gives thanks he has already received on the invisible and makes active preparation

02:16:05.932 --> 02:16:12.272
for receiving on the visible. One of my students was in need of a financial demonstration.

02:16:12.612 --> 02:16:19.392
She came to me and asked why it was not completed. I replied, perhaps you are in the habit of leaving

02:16:19.392 --> 02:16:23.872
things unfinished and the subconscious has gotten into the habit of not completing.

02:16:24.712 --> 02:16:33.232
As the without, so the within. She said, you are right, I often begin things and never finish them.

02:16:34.252 --> 02:16:39.592
I'll go home and finish something I commenced weeks ago and I know it will be symbolic of my

02:16:39.592 --> 02:16:47.292
demonstration. So she sewed assiduously and the article was soon completed. Shortly thereafter,

02:16:47.292 --> 02:16:54.112
the money came in a most curious manner. Her husband was paid his salary twice that month.

02:16:54.492 --> 02:16:58.552
He told the people of their mistake and they sent word to keep it.

02:16:59.632 --> 02:17:05.932
One man asks, believing he must receive, for God creates his own channels.

02:17:07.032 --> 02:17:13.252
I have been sometimes asked, suppose one has several talents, how is he to know which one to

02:17:13.252 --> 02:17:21.412
choose? Demand to be shown definitely. Say, infinite spirit, give me a definite lead,

02:17:21.832 --> 02:17:28.852
reveal to me my perfect self-expression, show which talent I am to make use of now.

02:17:29.832 --> 02:17:35.972
I have known people to suddenly enter a new line of work and be fully equipped with little to no

02:17:35.972 --> 02:17:41.792
training, so make the statement, I am fully equipped for the divine plan of my life,

02:17:42.152 --> 02:17:48.892
and be fearless in grasping opportunities. Some people are cheerful givers, but bad receivers.

02:17:49.472 --> 02:17:55.652
They refuse gifts through pride, or some negative reason, thereby blocking their channels,

02:17:56.092 --> 02:17:59.612
and invariably find themselves eventually with little or nothing.

02:18:00.472 --> 02:18:07.552
For example, a woman who had given away a great deal of money had a gift offered her of several

02:18:07.552 --> 02:18:13.812
thousand dollars. She refused to take it, saying she did not need it. Shortly thereafter, her

02:18:13.812 --> 02:18:20.192
finances were tied up, and she found herself in debt for that amount. Man should receive

02:18:20.192 --> 02:18:26.632
gracefully the bread returning to him upon the water. Freely ye have given, freely ye shall

02:18:26.632 --> 02:18:33.532
receive. There is always the perfect balance of giving and receiving, and though man should give

02:18:33.532 --> 02:18:39.892
without thinking of returns, he violates law if he does not accept the returns which come to him,

02:18:40.112 --> 02:18:44.732
for all gifts are from God, man being merely the channel.

02:18:46.992 --> 02:18:50.652
A thought of lack should never be held over the giver.

02:18:50.652 --> 02:18:58.452
For example, when the man gave me one cent, I did not say, Poor man, he cannot afford to

02:18:58.452 --> 02:19:06.452
give me that. I saw him rich and prosperous with his supply pouring in. It was this thought which

02:19:06.452 --> 02:19:14.052
brought it. If one has been a bad receiver, he must become a good one, and take even a postage

02:19:14.052 --> 02:19:18.232
stamp of it as given him, and open up his channels for receiving.

02:19:19.632 --> 02:19:25.692
The Lord loveth a cheerful receiver, as well as a cheerful giver. I have often been asked

02:19:25.692 --> 02:19:32.132
why one man is born rich and healthy, and another poor and sick. Where there is an effect,

02:19:32.212 --> 02:19:39.032
there is always a cause, there is no such thing as chance. This question is answered through the law

02:19:39.032 --> 02:19:45.552
of reincarnation. Man goes through many births and deaths until he knows the truth which sets

02:19:45.552 --> 02:19:53.692
him free. He is drawn back to the earth plane through unsatisfied desire to pay his karmic debts

02:19:53.692 --> 02:20:01.212
or to fulfill his destiny. The man born rich and healthy has had pictures in his subconscious mind,

02:20:01.572 --> 02:20:07.752
in his past life of health and riches, and the poor and sick man of disease and poverty.

02:20:08.792 --> 02:20:13.592
Man manifests, on any plane, the sum total of his subconscious beliefs.

02:20:14.572 --> 02:20:21.492
However, birth and death are man-made laws, for the wages of sin is death. The Adamic fall

02:20:21.492 --> 02:20:28.372
in consciousness through the belief in two powers. The real man, spiritual man, is birthless

02:20:28.372 --> 02:20:35.912
and deathless. He was never born and has never died. As he was in the beginning, he is now

02:20:35.912 --> 02:20:43.452
and shall ever be. So through the truth, man is set free from the law of karma, sin and death,

02:20:43.872 --> 02:20:50.932
and manifests the man made in his image and likeness. Man's freedom comes through

02:20:50.932 --> 02:20:56.572
fulfilling his destiny, bringing into manifestation the divine design of his life.

02:20:57.452 --> 02:21:03.992
His Lord will say unto him, Well done, thou good and faithful servant. Thou hast been faithful

02:21:03.992 --> 02:21:09.692
over a few things. I will make thee ruler over many things, death itself.

02:21:10.492 --> 02:21:14.832
Enter thou into the joy of thy Lord, eternal life.

02:21:51.693 --> 02:21:57.653
X. DENIALS AND AFFIRMATIONS.

02:21:57.653 --> 02:22:03.553
Thou shalt also decree a thing, and it shall be established unto thee.

02:22:04.933 --> 02:22:11.213
All the good that is to be made manifest in man's life is already an accomplished fact

02:22:11.213 --> 02:22:16.473
in divine mind, and is released through man's recognition or spoken word.

02:22:16.793 --> 02:22:23.853
So he must be careful to decree that only the divine idea be made manifest, for often

02:22:23.853 --> 02:22:28.673
he decrees, through his idle words, failure or misfortune.

02:22:29.693 --> 02:22:35.733
It is therefore of the utmost importance to word one's demands correctly, as stated

02:22:35.733 --> 02:22:37.253
in a previous chapter.

02:22:37.873 --> 02:22:43.953
If one desires a home, friend, position, or any other good thing, make the demand for

02:22:43.953 --> 02:22:45.533
the divine selection.

02:22:45.533 --> 02:22:53.693
For example, Infinite Spirit, open the way for my right home, my right friend, my right

02:22:53.693 --> 02:22:54.353
position.

02:22:55.053 --> 02:23:00.933
I give thanks that it now manifests under grace in a perfect way.

02:23:02.113 --> 02:23:05.393
The latter part of this statement is most important.

02:23:05.993 --> 02:23:09.853
For example, I knew a woman who demanded a thousand dollars.

02:23:09.853 --> 02:23:15.813
Her daughter was injured and they received a thousand dollars indemnity, so it did not

02:23:15.813 --> 02:23:17.553
come in a perfect way.

02:23:18.233 --> 02:23:20.933
The demand should have been worded in this way.

02:23:21.313 --> 02:23:27.133
Infinite Spirit, I give thanks that the one thousand dollars which is mine by divine right

02:23:27.133 --> 02:23:31.973
is now released and reaches me under grace in a perfect way.

02:23:32.913 --> 02:23:38.773
As one grows in a financial consciousness, he should demand that the enormous sums of

02:23:38.773 --> 02:23:44.573
which are his by divine right, reach him under grace in perfect ways.

02:23:45.573 --> 02:23:51.473
It is impossible for man to release more than he thinks is possible, for one is bound by

02:23:51.473 --> 02:23:54.553
the limited expectancies of the subconscious.

02:23:55.153 --> 02:24:00.133
He must enlarge his expectancies in order to receive in a larger way.

02:24:00.993 --> 02:24:03.953
Man so often limits himself and his demands.

02:24:03.953 --> 02:24:09.693
For example, a student made the demands for six hundred dollars by a certain date.

02:24:10.193 --> 02:24:16.853
He did receive it, but heard afterwards that he came very near receiving a thousand dollars,

02:24:17.193 --> 02:24:22.173
but he was given just six hundred as a result of his spoken word.

02:24:23.473 --> 02:24:26.293
They limited the Holy One of Israel.

02:24:27.153 --> 02:24:29.113
Wealth is a matter of consciousness.

02:24:29.853 --> 02:24:33.213
The French have a legend giving an example of this.

02:24:34.013 --> 02:24:38.673
A poor man was walking along a road when he met a traveler who stopped him and said,

02:24:39.233 --> 02:24:41.453
My good friend, I see that you are poor.

02:24:41.993 --> 02:24:45.533
Take this gold nugget, sell it, and you will be rich all your days.

02:24:46.193 --> 02:24:50.273
The man was overjoyed at his good fortune and took the nugget home.

02:24:50.893 --> 02:24:55.593
He immediately found work and became so prosperous that he did not sell the nugget.

02:24:56.313 --> 02:24:59.973
Years passed and he became a very rich man.

02:25:00.713 --> 02:25:02.973
One day he met a poor man on the road.

02:25:03.353 --> 02:25:04.873
He stopped him and said,

02:25:05.413 --> 02:25:11.893
My good friend, I will give you this gold nugget, which, if you sell, will make you rich for life.

02:25:12.813 --> 02:25:17.953
The mendicant took the nugget, had it valued, and found it was only brass.

02:25:18.613 --> 02:25:25.013
So we see the first man became rich through feeling rich, thinking the nugget was gold.

02:25:26.253 --> 02:25:29.773
Every man has within him a gold nugget.

02:25:30.173 --> 02:25:36.173
It is his consciousness of gold, of opulence, which brings riches into his life.

02:25:36.813 --> 02:25:40.893
In making his demands, man begins at his journey's end.

02:25:41.033 --> 02:25:44.493
That is, he declares he has already received.

02:25:45.713 --> 02:25:48.553
Before ye call, I shall answer.

02:25:49.693 --> 02:25:54.453
Continually affirming establishes the belief in the subconscious.

02:25:55.593 --> 02:26:01.173
It would not be necessary to make an affirmation more than once if one had perfect faith.

02:26:01.993 --> 02:26:08.333
One should not plead or supplicate, but give thanks repeatedly that he has received.

02:26:09.233 --> 02:26:13.473
The desert shall rejoice and blossom as the rose.

02:26:14.693 --> 02:26:21.113
This rejoicing, which is yet in the desert, state of consciousness, opens the way for release.

02:26:21.653 --> 02:26:25.833
The Lord's Prayer is in the form of command and demand.

02:26:26.533 --> 02:26:31.413
Give us this day our daily bread and forgive us our debts as we forgive our debtors.

02:26:31.913 --> 02:26:33.213
And ends in praise.

02:26:33.993 --> 02:26:37.133
For thine is the kingdom and the power and the glory forever.

02:26:37.673 --> 02:26:38.133
Amen.

02:26:39.673 --> 02:26:42.933
Concerning the works of my hands, command ye me.

02:26:44.053 --> 02:26:49.273
So prayer is command and demand, praise and thanksgiving.

02:26:49.933 --> 02:26:55.633
The student's work is in making himself believe that, with God, all things are possible.

02:26:57.173 --> 02:26:59.713
This is easy enough to state in the abstract,

02:26:59.953 --> 02:27:02.713
but a little more difficult when confronted with a problem.

02:27:03.253 --> 02:27:08.973
For example, it was necessary for a woman to demonstrate a large sum of money within a stated

02:27:08.973 --> 02:27:16.253
time. She knew she must do something to get a realization, for realization is manifestation,

02:27:16.733 --> 02:27:23.553
and she demanded a lead. She was walking through a department store when she saw a very beautiful

02:27:23.553 --> 02:27:29.933
pink enamel paper cutter. She felt the pull towards it. The thought came,

02:27:30.793 --> 02:27:36.593
I haven't a paper cutter good enough to open letters containing large checks.

02:27:37.773 --> 02:27:42.633
So she bought the paper cutter, which the reasoning mind would have called an extravagance.

02:27:43.153 --> 02:27:49.753
When she held it in her hand, she had a flash of a picture of herself opening an envelope

02:27:49.753 --> 02:27:54.733
containing a large check, and within a few weeks she received the money.

02:27:55.273 --> 02:27:58.833
The pink paper cutter was her bridge of active faith.

02:28:01.153 --> 02:28:05.753
Many stories are told of the power of the subconscious when directed in faith.

02:28:06.493 --> 02:28:12.393
For example, a man was spending the night in a farmhouse. The windows of the room had been

02:28:12.393 --> 02:28:17.753
nailed down, and in the middle of the night he felt suffocated and made his way in the dark to

02:28:17.753 --> 02:28:25.273
the window. He could not open it, so he smashed the pane with his fist, drew in draughts of fine,

02:28:25.353 --> 02:28:32.493
fresh air, and had a wonderful night's sleep. The next morning he found he had smashed the glass of

02:28:32.493 --> 02:28:39.793
a bookcase, and the window had remained closed during the whole night. He had supplied himself

02:28:39.793 --> 02:28:46.773
with oxygen simply by his thought of oxygen. When a student starts out to demonstrate,

02:28:47.133 --> 02:28:54.133
he should never turn back. Let not that man who wavers think that he shall receive anything of

02:28:54.133 --> 02:29:01.533
the Lord. A student once made this wonderful statement. When I ask the father for anything,

02:29:01.753 --> 02:29:08.273
I put my foot down and I say, Father, I'll take nothing less than I've asked for, but more.

02:29:09.233 --> 02:29:17.933
So man should never compromise. Having done all, stand. This is sometimes the most difficult time

02:29:17.933 --> 02:29:26.473
of demonstrating. The temptation comes to give up, to turn back, to compromise. He also serves

02:29:26.473 --> 02:29:34.593
who only stands and waits. Demonstrations often come at the eleventh hour because man then lets

02:29:34.593 --> 02:29:40.293
go, that is, stops reasoning, and infinite intelligence has a chance to work.

02:29:42.473 --> 02:29:49.973
Man's dreary desires are answered drearily and his impatient desires long delayed or violently

02:29:49.973 --> 02:29:58.573
fulfilled. For example, a woman asked me why it was she was constantly losing or breaking her glasses.

02:29:59.493 --> 02:30:03.493
We found she often said to herself and others with vexation,

02:30:04.113 --> 02:30:10.313
I wish I could get rid of my glasses. So her impatient desire was violently fulfilled.

02:30:11.093 --> 02:30:17.353
What she should have demanded was perfect eyesight, but what she registered in the subconscious was

02:30:17.353 --> 02:30:23.013
simply the impatient desire to be rid of her glasses, so they were continually being broken or

02:30:23.013 --> 02:30:31.353
lost. Two attitudes of mind cause loss. Depreciation, as in the case of the woman

02:30:31.353 --> 02:30:38.713
who did not appreciate her husband, or fear of loss, which makes a picture of loss in the subconscious.

02:30:39.853 --> 02:30:46.233
When a student is able to let go of his problem, cast his burden, he will have instantaneous

02:30:46.233 --> 02:30:54.073
manifestation. For example, a woman was out during a very stormy day and her umbrella was blown

02:30:54.073 --> 02:31:00.493
inside out. She was about to make a call on some people whom she had never met and she did not wish

02:31:00.493 --> 02:31:06.213
to make her first appearance with a dilapidated umbrella. She could not throw it away as it did

02:31:06.213 --> 02:31:14.453
not belong to her. So in desperation she exclaimed, Oh God, you take charge of this umbrella. I don't

02:31:14.453 --> 02:31:21.853
know what to do. A moment later a voice behind her said, Lady, do you want your umbrella mended?

02:31:22.853 --> 02:31:32.813
There stood an umbrella mender. She replied, Indeed I do. The man mended the umbrella while

02:31:32.813 --> 02:31:38.373
she went into the house to pay her call and when she returned she had a good umbrella.

02:31:39.173 --> 02:31:46.373
So there is always an umbrella mender at hand on man's pathway when one puts the umbrella

02:31:46.373 --> 02:31:53.293
or situation in God's hands. One should always follow a denial with an affirmation.

02:31:53.373 --> 02:31:58.893
For example, I was called on the phone late one night to treat a man whom I had never seen.

02:31:59.113 --> 02:32:06.413
He was apparently very ill. I made the statement, I deny the appearance of disease. It is unreal.

02:32:06.413 --> 02:32:13.753
Therefore cannot register in his consciousness. This man is a perfect idea in divine mind,

02:32:14.153 --> 02:32:22.253
pure substance expressing perfection. There is no time or space in divine mind. Therefore

02:32:22.253 --> 02:32:29.653
the word reaches instantly its destination and does not return void. I have treated patience in

02:32:29.653 --> 02:32:35.853
Europe and have found that the result was instantaneous. I am asked so often the

02:32:36.413 --> 02:32:43.273
visualizing and visioning. Visualizing is a mental process governed by the reasoning or

02:32:43.273 --> 02:32:51.193
conscious mind. Visioning is a spiritual process governed by intuition or the super conscious mind.

02:32:52.093 --> 02:32:58.793
The student should train his mind to receive these flashes of inspiration and work out the divine

02:32:58.793 --> 02:33:07.113
pictures through definite leads. When a man can say, I desire only that which God desires for me,

02:33:07.813 --> 02:33:12.973
his false desires fade from the consciousness and a new set of blueprints is given him by

02:33:12.973 --> 02:33:19.593
the master architect, the God within. God's plan for each man transcends the limitation of

02:33:19.593 --> 02:33:26.493
the reasoning mind and is always the square of life containing health, wealth, love and perfect

02:33:26.493 --> 02:33:33.273
self-expression. Many a man is building for himself in imagination a bungalow when he

02:33:33.273 --> 02:33:41.173
should be building a palace. If a student tries to force a demonstration through the reasoning mind,

02:33:41.573 --> 02:33:49.193
he brings it to a standstill. I will hasten, saith the Lord. He should act only through intuition

02:33:49.193 --> 02:33:57.453
or definite leads. Rest in the Lord and wait patiently. Trust also in him and he will bring

02:33:57.453 --> 02:34:06.653
it to pass. I have seen the law work in the most astonishing manner. For example, a student stated

02:34:06.653 --> 02:34:12.253
that it was necessary for her to have a hundred dollars by the following day. It was a debt of

02:34:12.253 --> 02:34:19.293
vital importance which had to be met. I spoke the word, declaring spirit was never too late

02:34:19.293 --> 02:34:26.173
and that the supply was at hand. That evening she phoned me of the miracle. She said that the

02:34:26.173 --> 02:34:33.673
thought came to her to go to her safety deposit box at the bank to examine some papers. She looked

02:34:33.673 --> 02:34:41.153
over the papers and at the bottom of the box was a new one hundred dollar bill. She was astounded

02:34:41.153 --> 02:34:47.633
and she said she knew she had never put it there for she had gone through the papers many times.

02:34:48.313 --> 02:34:53.573
It may have been a materialization as Jesus Christ materialized the loaves and fishes.

02:34:54.553 --> 02:35:03.233
Man will reach the stage where his word is made flesh or materialized instantly. The fields ripe

02:35:03.233 --> 02:35:09.693
with the harvest will manifest immediately as in all of the miracles of Jesus Christ.

02:35:10.653 --> 02:35:17.493
There is a tremendous power alone in the name Jesus Christ. It stands for truth made manifest.

02:35:18.493 --> 02:35:26.653
He said whatsoever ye ask the father in my name he will give it to you. The power of this name

02:35:26.653 --> 02:35:33.333
raises the student into the fourth dimension where he is freed from all astral and psychic influences

02:35:33.333 --> 02:35:40.233
and he becomes unconditioned and absolute as God himself is unconditioned and absolute.

02:35:41.733 --> 02:35:49.013
I have seen many healings accomplished by using the words in the name of Jesus Christ. Christ was

02:35:49.013 --> 02:35:56.453
both person and principle and the Christ within each man is his redeemer and salvation. The Christ

02:35:56.453 --> 02:36:02.793
within is his own fourth dimensional self the man made in God's image and likeness.

02:36:03.273 --> 02:36:09.193
This is the self which has never failed never known sickness or sorrow was never born and

02:36:09.193 --> 02:36:17.213
has never died. It is the resurrection and the life of each man. No man cometh to the father

02:36:17.213 --> 02:36:25.173
saved by the son means that God the universal working on the place of the particular becomes

02:36:25.173 --> 02:36:34.273
the Christ in man and the Holy Ghost means God in action. So daily man is manifesting

02:36:34.273 --> 02:36:41.773
the trinity of the father son and Holy Ghost. Man should make an art of thinking. The master

02:36:41.773 --> 02:36:47.933
thinker is an artist and is careful to paint only the divine designs upon the canvas of his mind

02:36:47.933 --> 02:36:53.933
and he paints these pictures with masterly strokes of power and decision having perfect

02:36:53.933 --> 02:36:59.773
faith that there is no power to mar their perfection and that they shall manifest in

02:36:59.773 --> 02:37:07.313
his life the ideal made real. All power is given man through right thinking to bring his heaven

02:37:07.313 --> 02:37:16.333
upon his earth and this is the goal of the game of life. The simple rules are fearless faith,

02:37:16.333 --> 02:37:25.453
non-resistance and love. May each reader be now freed from that thing which has held him

02:37:25.453 --> 02:37:33.293
in bondage through the ages standing between him and his own and know the truth which makes

02:37:33.293 --> 02:37:42.613
him free. Free to fulfill his destiny to bring into manifestation the divine design of his life

02:37:42.613 --> 02:37:47.073
health, wealth, love and perfect self-expression.

02:37:48.733 --> 02:37:52.853
Be ye transformed by the renewing of your mind.

02:38:29.935 --> 02:38:31.055
FOR PROSPERITY

02:38:32.135 --> 02:38:41.115
God is my unfailing supply, and large sums of money come to me quickly, under grace, in perfect ways.

02:38:42.775 --> 02:38:45.255
FOR RIGHT CONDITIONS

02:38:45.255 --> 02:38:54.715
Every plan my Father in heaven has not planned shall be dissolved and dissipated, and the Divine Idea now comes to pass.

02:38:56.675 --> 02:38:59.535
FOR RIGHT CONDITIONS

02:38:59.535 --> 02:39:05.595
Only that which is true of God is true of me, for I and the Father are one.

02:39:07.815 --> 02:39:08.895
FOR FAITH

02:39:08.895 --> 02:39:19.615
As I am one with God, I am one with my good, for God is both the giver and the gift. I cannot separate the giver from the gift.

02:39:21.395 --> 02:39:23.535
FOR RIGHT CONDITIONS

02:39:23.535 --> 02:39:30.675
Divine Love now dissolves and dissipates every wrong condition in my mind, body, and affairs.

02:39:32.395 --> 02:39:38.895
Divine Love is the most powerful chemical in the universe, and dissolves everything which is not of itself.

02:39:41.095 --> 02:39:42.575
FOR HEALTH

02:39:42.575 --> 02:39:49.815
Divine Love fills my consciousness with health, and every cell in my body is filled with light.

02:39:50.695 --> 02:39:51.935
FOR THE EYESIGHT

02:39:51.935 --> 02:40:05.755
My eyes are God's eyes. I see with the eyes of Spirit. I see clearly the open way. There are no obstacles on my pathway. I see clearly the perfect plan.

02:40:07.515 --> 02:40:09.155
FOR GUIDANCE

02:40:09.155 --> 02:40:17.035
I am divinely sensitive to my intuitive leads, and give instant obedience to Thy will.

02:40:20.155 --> 02:40:21.395
FOR THE HEARING

02:40:21.395 --> 02:40:34.015
My ears are God's ears. I hear with the ears of Spirit. I am non-resistant, and am willing to be led. I hear glad tidings of great joy.

02:40:36.035 --> 02:40:37.395
FOR RIGHT WORK

02:40:37.395 --> 02:40:45.195
I have a perfect work in a perfect way. I give a perfect service for a perfect pay.

02:40:47.095 --> 02:40:49.115
FOR FREEDOM FROM ALL BONDAGE

02:40:49.115 --> 02:40:54.115
I cast this burden on the Christ within, and I go free.
